INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('15', '2', '2012-08-28 16:35:09', '2012-08-28 16:35:09', 'As a provider of comprehensive corporate wellness programs for more than a decade, Sterling Wellness Solutions is a proven leader in the industry.  We work with clients to create a customized approach to building a culture of wellness within their organizations.  Our fully integrated software program, Health Park, can provide a plan to fit the needs and budget of any size group. Utilizing our combined onsite, online and telephonic approach, we can provide health screenings and assessments, personal health coaching, educational support and incentive programs that can affect your bottom line.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSterling’s mission is reflected in the commitment, passion and experience of our team.  Under the leadership of owner and president, Claire Kelbaugh, alongside our Medical Director, Dr. Stephen Cannon, our professionals include registered nurses, registered dietitians, fitness experts, personal trainers, certified wellness experts and health coaches, with the support of a complete administrative staff and communications team.  Our health coaches are degreed professionals with additional certifications from the Cooper Institute, a nationally recognized training program based on research in the areas of health and fitness best-practices.  Members of our team also have certifications from WELCOA, National Wellness Institute, NSCA, ACSM and more.  Our commitment to service and our goal to provide a professional and positive experience for every participant remains a part of our daily operations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Mission Statement-</em></strong>\r\n\r\nSterling Wellness Solutions is committed to positively affecting the health and well-being of workplace populations to impact the productivity and success of our client companies.  Our dedicated team of practitioners serves to deliver comprehensive wellness services to our client partnerships and their employees t