INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('73', '2', '2012-08-28 17:07:21', '2012-08-28 17:07:21', '<ul>\n	<li>When will I get my results?\n<ul>\n	<li>Any participant who registers alert levels will be contacted within 36 hours to seek immediate treatment from a physician.  All other participants will learn more about their results through an onsite or telephone review of their results.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Do I need a doctor’s orders?\n<ul>\n	<li>Nope! You can simply call Sterling Labs at 1-800-838-0337, or order online. You will be emailed a requisition form that can be printed and taken to any Sterling-contracted lab facility nearest you.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Will someone be available to help me understand my results?\n<ul>\n	<li>A certified health coach or nurse will review your results through a telephone or onsite review. A health coach can be contacted during regular business hours Monday-Friday 8am-5pm.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>How do I order a direct access lab test?\n<ul>\n	<li>Ordering is easy.  Follow these steps:</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\nSelect the lab tests you would like to order.  Click on a category in the left hand column to see a full list of available tests.  If you know the name of the test you need, use the search feature to search for test by name.\nAdd the selected test(s) to the shopping cart, and continue shopping to select additional tests.\nIf you have a discount screening code, enter it at the bottom of the screen.\nProceed to checkout.\nNew users, register as a new customer, and complete your personal information.\nReturning users, enter your user name and password.\nAccept the terms and conditions.  (Access the complete terms and conditions in the left hand column.)\n\nPrint your requisition form to bring with you for testing.\n\nLocate a participating lab near you.\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Note:  Change the button to say “Register as a new customer to complete your order.”</span>', 'FAQ Lab Questions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '72-revision', '', '', '2012-08-28 17:07:21', '2012-08-28 17:07:21', '', '72', 'http://delica.websitewelcome.com/~sterling/?p=73', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
