INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('391', '1', '2012-08-28 16:55:36', '2012-08-28 16:55:36', 'Our customized web-based portal, Health Park, ensures that your wellness activities aren’t limited to an onsite screening.  It’s important to carry the message of health and wellness over the course of the year.\r\n\r\nOur customizable service packages are available at three levels: Essentials, Elite and Exclusive. Programs can include the Health Risk Assessment (HRA), Health Coaching, Health Education and Communication, Incentive Programs, and Wellness Consulting services. Services are offered onsite, online and via telephone. Our unique web-based approach coupled with the human touch of our staff, provides the tools to implement and manage a successful wellness program that continuously motivates individuals to lead a healthy lifestyle. The Health Park Program is designed to offer ongoing assistance with designing, planning, promotion and implementation so that each program continuously grows each year. Health Park can also provide education through interactive action plans focused on key health risk factors.  Health challenges and other events can also be managed through Health Park, with the ability to track participation and earn incentive points.  Participants also have access to a customized Personal HRA report and a Personal Electronic Health Record.\r\n\r\nPart of the approach to building a culture of wellness in your business must start from within your organization. Sterling Wellness will help educate you, the business owner, and your wellness coordinator about how to build a culture of wellness. Creating an atmosphere of peer support where healthy choices become commonplace is vital to a successful program.\r\n\r\nSterling Wellness will support the buy-in of the company’s leadership through our health education materials and program promotion and communication. The Health Park program is available at three levels from a basic start-up program to the most comprehensive package. Your business and your employees will benefit from an improved quality of life and increased productivity.', 'Health Management Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '56-revision-2', '', '', '2012-08-28 16:55:36', '2012-08-28 16:55:36', '', '56', 'http://delica.websitewelcome.com/~sterling/56-revision-2/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
