INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('437', '1', '2012-09-24 18:07:01', '2012-09-24 18:07:01', '<h2>Our difference is our singular commitment to wellness\r\n— all day, every day.</h2>\r\nThese days, information about wellness is everywhere. Readily available from your insurance provider, your local hospital, the community fitness center, you name it…. Our difference is our singular commitment to wellness - all day, every day. Our only focus is the engagement of your employee population in the practice of healthy living and impacting your bottom line.\r\n\r\nSince 2001, Sterling Wellness Solutions has been dedicated to reducing the costs of healthcare by educating employees and their dependents about how to manage their health risk factors. With more than 25 employees including our Medical Director, nurses, health coaches and dietitians, Sterling serves the national market with the intent of improving the quality of life for all program participants. Sterling Wellness supplies a full range of experts to address the needs of your company and your employees.\r\n\r\nWe know wellness because we’ve been doing it for over a decade. Our client list includes organizations in a wide variety of industries with multiple locations throughout the U.S., ranging in size from 50-26,000 employees.\r\n\r\nOur goal for every client is to reduce healthcare costs and keep individuals out of the hospital, ultimately improving the employee’s quality of life, decreasing absenteeism and increasing productivity, morale and longevity. Our clients report reductions in emergency room visits, success in smoking cessation programs, and increased awareness and care for those with disease states, just to name a few. In many cases, Sterling’s onsite visit has helped identify early warning stages for at-risk individuals, allowing for treatment and intervention.\r\n\r\nOur comprehensive approach can give you the tools needed to support your efforts to build a healthier, more productive workforce. The reality is, wellness often requires a culture change in the corporate environment. To be effective, the effort must start at the top with the support of upper management and all involved in administering the program. Peer support built among co-workers and driven by group participation in goal-setting and health challenges is also vital. At Sterling Wellness, we can help you develop and implement a plan that will empower your employees to adopt a healthier lifestyle.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Why Sterling Wellness?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-10', '', '', '2012-09-24 18:07:01', '2012-09-24 18:07:01', '', '20', 'http://delica.websitewelcome.com/~sterling/20-revision-10/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('438', '1', '2012-09-24 18:18:29', '2012-09-24 18:18:29', '<h2>We plan for date night. We plan for vacations. We plan for retirement. Make plans today for a long and healthy life by participating in your employer’s wellness program.</h2>\r\nThe heart and soul of any successful company is its employees. In the digital age of technology, we have engineered physical activity out of our lives. Urgent deadlines, long commutes, and frequent stressors have burdened our lifestyles, limiting the amount of focus one can put toward improving or maintaining health.\r\n\r\nYour health and well-being is about more than numbers on a scale or blood pressure cuff. It’s about finding your motivation in life. It’s being in optimal health to enjoy retirement or having energy to chase grandkids. It’s about being your best at home and on the job. Sterling Wellness Solutions is here to provide you with the tools and resources you need to function at your best. As a participant in our program, you will have direct access to lifestyle intervention, goal-setting and motivational change through our team of experienced heath coaches. Our unique online programs coupled with the support of our coaching staff will allow you to set goals for small changes, working toward a greater accomplishment. In collaboration with your colleagues, we will work to determine the needs and interests of your workplace, ultimately creating an environment that offers opportunities for optimal well-being.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Benefits To Employees', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-3', '', '', '2012-09-24 18:18:29', '2012-09-24 18:18:29', '', '26', 'http://delica.websitewelcome.com/~sterling/26-revision-3/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
