INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1377', '14', '2012-11-06 21:02:36', '2012-11-06 21:02:36', '<h2>Impacting Wellness\r\nOne Employee at a Time</h2>\r\n<blockquote>The greatest success can be found in the stories of the many people who are touched by our programs.   We have helped clients lower blood pressure, lose weight, reduce medications, and quit smoking. Here are some of their stories.</blockquote>\r\n“The health of our employees has been invaluably impacted through our partnership with the Primary Care Program. The onsite interaction between the Sterling Wellness Primary Care Nurse and our employee population has enriched the overall wellness culture of our organization. Sterling’s ongoing health initiatives deliver a full spectrum of resources, education, and health coaching to inspire change among our employees. The personal and reputable relationship established between our employees and the Primary Care Nurse has enhanced the trust of our employees, allowing us to further the progression of this wellness program. Sterling’s proactive approach to wellness has undeniably affected our bottom line by identifying ways to reduce risks, and by implementing programs that have offered a positive return.”\r\n<strong><em>- Company CFO, New Orleans, LA area</em></strong>\r\n\r\n“Advanced Plan for Health has worked with Sterling Wellness for five years, where we have worked jointly as a team to improve the health of employees and dependents of an employer group. Through the collaborative efforts of the client’s group health plan management team, the client has experienced an estimated savings of $2,800,000, based on the client’s costs and annual cost trend as compared to national medical cost trend. During this same time period, the quality of health care provided to the population has improved by 25-30%, as measured by Plan participants’ compliance with preventive medicine and chronic illness management metrics. Sterling Wellness works effectively with the team, proactively responds to available information, and develops and implements creative and effective approaches to working with and motivating employees and their families to improve their health.”\r\n\r\n<em>-<strong>Joy McGee-Cory, Advanced Plan for Health</strong></em>', 'Client Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-20', '', '', '2012-11-06 21:02:36', '2012-11-06 21:02:36', '', '22', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/22-revision-20/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1378', '14', '2012-10-30 19:52:24', '2012-10-30 19:52:24', '<h2>Putting the Pieces of the\r\nPuzzle Together</h2>\r\n<blockquote>A successful wellness program starts with a vision for culture change. Sterling Wellness Solutions can help create a culture of wellness for any business through our comprehensive approach. With wellness champions and senior leadership involved, draft a vision, plan, and timeline.</blockquote>\r\nOur fully integrated software program, Health Park, can provide a customized plan to fit your needs and budget. Utilizing our combined onsite, online and telephonic approach, we can provide health screenings and assessments, personal health coaching, educational support and incentive programs that can affect your bottom line.\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Our services include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Program design and management</li>\r\n	<li>Private or group screening results, goal setting, and health education programs</li>\r\n	<li>Health coaching</li>\r\n	<li>Incentive tracking and program development</li>\r\n	<li>Health Park technology solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Program promotion and communications</li>\r\n	<li>Third party vendor integration</li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive aggregate reporting</li>\r\n	<li>HIPAA Compliance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>', 'Getting Started', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '52-revision-17', '', '', '2012-10-30 19:52:24', '2012-10-30 19:52:24', '', '52', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/52-revision-17/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1379', '14', '2012-10-04 16:35:15', '2012-10-04 16:35:15', '<h2>Health Coaching:\r\nMotivating Lifestyle Change</h2>\r\n<blockquote>Our health coaching services are an integral part of the transition to a healthy lifestyle.  Once health information has been collected from your employee population, Sterling’s Health Coaches can stratify low, moderate and high risk populations, and target them appropriately throughout the year.</blockquote>\r\nMost companies opt for at least quarterly contact with these individuals to provide a personalized approach to adopting a healthier lifestyle, while monitoring progress and encouraging compliance for disease management.\r\n\r\nOur health coaches are degreed professionals with additional certifications from the Cooper Institute, a nationally recognized training program based on research in the areas of health and fitness best-practices.  Members of our team also have certifications from WELCOA, National Wellness Institute, NSCA, ACSM and more. Our full-time staff of nurses, health coaches and dietitians complete monthly continuing education credits, and attend quarterly in-service sessions. All health coaches are CPR/AED certified.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/who-we-are/health-coach-profiles/\">Meet Our Health Coaches</a>', 'Health Coaching', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-revision-14', '', '', '2012-10-04 16:35:15', '2012-10-04 16:35:15', '', '61', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/61-revision-14/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1380', '14', '2012-10-30 20:00:43', '2012-10-30 20:00:43', '<a href=\"http://bit.ly/PHFstx\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-1295\" title=\"Click here to log on to Health Park! \" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/health-park-004.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"305\" height=\"171\" /></a>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-left: 270px;\"> <strong>Wellness 24 / 7</strong></h2>\r\n<blockquote>Sterling’s Health Park Program provides participants with access to the tools and support that can truly impact overall well-being.</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">                                             <a href=\"http://bit.ly/PHFstx\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1234 alignnone\" title=\"HP-login\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/HP-login.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"216\" height=\"48\" /></a></p>\r\nSterling Wellness Solutions utilizes web-based technology for delivery of online wellness services as a component of our total wellness approach.  The Health Park portal allows program participants to have access to their wellness initiative anytime, anywhere, in a secure environment that protects personal health information.  Health Park provides access to wellness beginning with a Health Risk Assessment. A customized report coupled with access to our certified health coaches and nursing staff, can provide a platform for lifestyle change.  Interactive education through online action plans can reinforce the message of healthy living, while health challenges provide opportunities for engagement and change. Participants also have access to a Personal Electronic Health Record, encouraging them to take control of their health care.  The Health Park program also allows Sterling to track and manage company incentive programs, giving participants access to their rewards and points.<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/iStock_000020632575Small.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-409\" title=\"Couple using a laptop.\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/iStock_000020632575Small-e1351281963501-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSterling’s health coaching team also utilizes Health Park to engage employees in their personal health journey, track the progress of participants, and interact in a secure, web-based environment.', 'Web Based Tools', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '63-revision-51', '', '', '2012-10-30 20:00:43', '2012-10-30 20:00:43', '', '63', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/63-revision-51/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1381', '14', '2012-11-06 21:49:41', '2012-11-06 21:49:41', '<h1><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-1295\" title=\"Click here to log on to Health Park! \" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/health-park-004.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"244\" height=\"137\" />Tools and Support that Impact Well-Being</h1>\r\n<blockquote>Sterling Wellness Solutions utilizes web-based technology for delivery of online wellness services as a component of our total wellness approach.  Sterling\'s Health Park program provides participants with access to interactive tools that reinforce the message of healthy living.</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">                                             <a href=\"http://bit.ly/PHFstx\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1234 alignnone\" title=\"HP-login\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/HP-login.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"216\" height=\"48\" /></a></p>\r\nThe Health Park portal allows program participants to have access to their wellness initiative anytime, anywhere, in a secure environment that protects personal health information. Sterling’s health coaching team also utilizes Health Park to engage employees in their personal health journey, track the progress of participants, and interact in a secure, web-based environment.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-409\" title=\"Couple using a laptop.\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/iStock_000020632575Small-e1351281963501.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"201\" />\r\n<h3>Wellness 24/7:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Health Risk Assessment</li>\r\n	<li>Personal Electronic Health Record</li>\r\n	<li>Online Action Plans</li>\r\n	<li>Tracking and Management of Incentive Programs</li>\r\n	<li>Secure Messaging</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-populated interface with Lab Results</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Web Based Tools', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '63-revision-52', '', '', '2012-11-06 21:49:41', '2012-11-06 21:49:41', '', '63', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/63-revision-52/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1382', '14', '2012-10-04 13:34:44', '2012-10-04 13:34:44', '<h2>High Impact With a Human Touch</h2>\r\n<blockquote>Employer wellness programs can have a tremendous impact on employee health, morale and productivity.</blockquote>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Prescription-Graphic1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-503\" title=\"Prescription-Graphic\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Prescription-Graphic1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"186\" height=\"238\" /></a>The key to a successful program is high participation and follow-up. Sterling’s Primary Care Program offers a high-touch approach to building a culture of wellness and addressing chronic disease states. A primary care program typically utilizes a nurse or certified health coach to address individual follow-up onsite, providing the highest level of support and education needed for lifestyle change.\r\n\r\nScheduled onsite visits not only target health risks among your employees, but also reinforce the habits of healthy members of your population.  Programming may include group seminars, scheduled individual consultations, blood pressure checks, weight and body measurements, complete health risk appraisals, general health education, management and monitoring of health challenges, and more. The primary care professional will also maintain a scheduled telephonic health coaching rotation to review health status, set realistic goals, oversee disease compliance, assist with medical questions, remind individuals about their preventive exams and promote and schedule the next onsite visit.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Primary Care Program', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '65-revision-11', '', '', '2012-10-04 13:34:44', '2012-10-04 13:34:44', '', '65', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/65-revision-11/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1383', '14', '2012-09-25 19:31:12', '2012-09-25 19:31:12', '<h2>We plan for date night. We plan for vacations. We plan for retirement. Make plans today for a long and healthy life by participating in your employer’s wellness program.</h2>\r\nThe heart and soul of any successful company is its employees. In the digital age of technology, we have engineered physical activity out of our lives. Urgent deadlines, long commutes, and frequent stressors have burdened our lifestyles, limiting the amount of focus one can put toward improving or maintaining health.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/exersize-graphic1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-505\" title=\"exersize-graphic\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/exersize-graphic1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"207\" height=\"195\" /></a>Your health and well-being is about more than numbers on a scale or blood pressure cuff. It’s about finding your motivation in life. It’s being in optimal health to enjoy retirement or having energy to chase grandkids. It’s about being your best at home and on the job. Sterling Wellness Solutions is here to provide you with the tools and resources you need to function at your best.\r\n<blockquote>As a participant in our program, you will have direct access to lifestyle intervention, goal-setting and motivational change through our team of experienced heath coaches.</blockquote>\r\nOur unique online programs coupled with the support of our coaching staff will allow you to set goals for small changes, working toward a greater accomplishment. In collaboration with your colleagues, we will work to determine the needs and interests of your workplace, ultimately creating an environment that offers opportunities for optimal well-being.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Benefits To Employees', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-12', '', '', '2012-09-25 19:31:12', '2012-09-25 19:31:12', '', '26', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/26-revision-12/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
