d training for a <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001MxSgJdEYHqEVkem4jhG3dYdxfxitzNwMKqhx0F5gCactnJY59retFFe1qqKJk_FAZaIkqNx2OGadVQZazEM9j4ks_UvcGOsHaX1eC-h2eXXBlYcGCyq9o4IynOfRw4vxItT-fpMacyTfQ3S1rZNJHyAcRSD8Jz2ZZQq8v17nYmQdgkli9Ji8kh3S5OKyb0RAAtUuYXlnM_3XDD1nmsJPgQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">heart walk</a>.\r\n\r\nVisit the American Heart Association\'s <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001MxSgJdEYHqFXNr7EU3PO7xgG82i_ZawcFY1CMhKhThdwhoEpBPM77zGDMLnPYhP3zodV9jodJx2AD9MDt5cdF53jjM90Ewa6HXxMwxOqhheXQHaM7mAy2bjJDQFTih9hTDuPC1_Z4CZr769dunNEaUnOabPgrccGozbObGV3FTVxtMnvJ-EySFH8a_ceNpNbAUvFhw51jj-B60cm294ElEd6YtN-rW7K\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Heart Walk</a> site to learn about community walks, events, and fundraisers to bring awareness to heart health and diabetes. Funds raised through Heart Walks will support research and lifesaving education for heart disease, stroke, and pediatric heart conditions. Rally the support of colleagues, family, and friends to join you on the walk. If you have trouble locating a Heart Walk in your community, find another 5k walk or race at <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001MxSgJdEYHqENGnC_Q3_GIfEcoBe8_U9KVVOCiurGNDwLCd7LbLx6BqDuGwRc8li4MfvSnmlY14dqaNgcFhXV8tgNTWrcmw08GjOs4Oi7Pc6SQQ5nnCKX7Q==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">active.com</a>.', 'Join the Movement this Walktober', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'join-the-movement-this-walktober', '', '', '2012-12-06 21:53:13', '2012-12-06 21:53:13', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1451', '0', 'post', '', '0');
