e body, and drastically increases the risk for heart disease, COPD, and multiple kinds of cancer. Join the estimated 46 million Americans that have quit smoking for good, and make', 'Finding the Resources to Quit', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1476-revision', '', '', '2012-12-06 22:20:59', '2012-12-06 22:20:59', '', '1476', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1476-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1478', '14', '2012-11-23 22:21:48', '2012-11-23 22:21:48', 'With so many delectable side dishes and a buffet of mouth-watering desserts, it may feel like the main attraction of your Thanksgiving meal gets neglected. When too much turkey ends up back in the refrigerator, transform your left over bird into one of these <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?t=nhu87rkab.0.tqhtoflab.otbu8wdab.2757&amp;ts=S0830&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fallrecipes.com%2Frecipes%2Fmeat-and-poultry%2Fturkey%2Fleftovers%2F\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">healthy dishes</a> from AllRecipes. Try turning your cold turkey into a veggie-loaded pot-pie, soup, casserole, or salad. For proper handling, prepare or freeze your left over turkey within 4 days of its original cooking date.  <!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1034\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:341.8pt;margin-top:336pt;width:165.75pt;height:108.75pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"https://imgssl.constantcontact.com/ui/stock2/thanksgiving-dinner.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"https://imgssl.constantcontact.com/ui/stock2/thanksgiving-dinner.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"221\" height=\"145\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->\r\n\r\nTurkey is a lean meat choice that is low in fat and high in protein. When possible, choose pieces without the skin, and keep portions around 2-3 ounces, or roughly the size of your palm. Turkey is a great source of iron, B vitamins, and zinc. Is the age-old adage true that turkey makes you sleepy? Although it contains tryptophan, an amino acid that regulates sleep, most meat, cheese, and nuts contain comparable levels. The sleep factor is likely due to a meal heavy in carbohydrates that spike blood sugar and cause the afternoon lull. Try taking a walk or playing an active game post-meal to prevent the groggy feeling.', 'Going Cold Turkey', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'going-cold-turkey', '', '', '2012-12-06 22:22:37', '2012-12-06 22:22:37', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1478', '0', 'post', '', '0');
