ion, and symptoms of Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS).\n\n<strong>Mint leaf</strong>- Often added as a garnish, the raw leaf can freshen breath and help digest a big meal.\n\n<strong>Peppermint tea</strong>- Brewing the leaves of the mint plant can release compounds that ease stomach discomfort, nausea, and aid in digestion.\n\n<strong>Menthol</strong>- Commonly used in topical creams and cosmetics, this form of mint has been known to soothe aching muscles and joints by providing a cooling sensation.\n\nAdd a sprig of mint to ice water for a refreshing taste, or add crushed leaves to your next chicken marinade. For more tummy taming recipes, visit <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001fIAtf8uEeUmhiEAr_B9y6bJBpOhrpDhiikKiSMsfwyaOEFBdHP3aSJLoLJvHDB7HPpFPucBKVHXj_xItrlDfz4lkGueFdWsUPbmZDvcCToKTva8ZzWVZ-4lj4hQVSLwQXR08U2Kd3QO4ZZUE8GeVhfGDQDtBR-pP\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Simply Recipes</a>.', 'The Power of Peppermint', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1486-revision', '', '', '2012-12-06 22:28:00', '2012-12-06 22:28:00', '', '1486', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1486-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1488', '14', '2012-12-14 22:28:40', '2012-12-14 22:28:40', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1040\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:0;margin-top:1015.5pt;width:71.25pt;height:105pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/373.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/373.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.373\" width=\"95\" height=\"140\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Over 80% of all infectious illnesses are transmitted by touch. According to the Centers for Disease Control, the single most important thing you can do to keep from getting sick is to wash your hands. Germs can easily enter the body by touching the eyes or nose, coming in contact with an infected person, or through food prepared with contaminated hands.\r\n\r\nWhen washing, remember to wash for 15-30 seconds under the nails, between fingers, and under rings. Once hands are completely dry, turn off the faucet and open the door with a paper towel to prevent recontaminating your hands. Alcohol based hand sanitizers work when a sink isn\'t available, but make sure they contain at least 60% alcohol and rub vigorously for 25 seconds. To respect others, sneeze into your elbow, and please stay home if you are sick to prevent the further spread of germs.', 'Stay Well this Flu Season', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'stay-well-this-flu-season-2', '', '', '2012-12-06 22:29:56', '2012-12-06 22:29:56', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1488', '0', 'post', '', '0');
