INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1519', '14', '2013-01-08 17:40:33', '2013-01-08 17:40:33', 'It\'s no surprise that being exposed to loud noises leads to hearing loss. Once you lose your hearing, you can\'t get it back without help from a hearing aid. Many people with hearing loss also have tinnitus, a ringing or high pitched sound in the ears. Although tinnitus can result from a number of causes such as allergies, stress, medications, or ear infections, it\'s often a result of over exposure to loud noise. To keep your auditory sense sharp, follow these rules:\r\n<ol start=\"1\">\r\n	<li><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1027\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:0;margin-top:544.5pt;width:90.75pt;height:131.25pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:7.5pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:7.5pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:7.5pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:7.5pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/381.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/381.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.381\" width=\"121\" height=\"175\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"10\" vspace=\"10\" /><!--[endif]-->Wear ear plugs when operating electric tools or heavy machinery, and mowing.</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid loud music from headphones, while driving, and live concerts.</li>\r\n	<li>Keep television sets, radios, and alarm clocks at a reasonable noise level.</li>\r\n	<li>Take breaks from sustained loud noises by moving to a quiet place.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nHearing loss can occur at a sustained noise level of 90-95 decibels. As a general rule of thumb, if you have to raise your voice to be heard, hearing loss can occur. For more information on hearing loss and tinnitus, visit the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001qel0SAE1-vK_U1Syrj1GWk7WwZRzNuEHmf-tPh_0_FmglrmbXW7S3dR0BLFZL2LTF1Q24Z0Iz4rEP4I27dYzMW0UoPfd0NdtY8cUWAjniOk=\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">House Ear Institute</a>.', 'Ringing in the New \'Ears', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ringing-in-the-new-ears', '', '', '2013-02-06 17:41:36', '2013-02-06 17:41:36', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1519', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1520', '14', '2013-02-06 17:41:10', '2013-02-06 17:41:10', '&nbsp;\n\nIt\'s no surprise that being exposed to loud noises leads to hearing loss. Once you lose your hearing, you can\'t get it back without help from a hearing aid. Many people with hearing loss also have tinnitus, a ringing or high pitched sound in the ears. Although tinnitus can result from a number of causes such as allergies, stress, medications, or ear infections, it\'s often a result of over exposure to loud noise. To keep your auditory sense sharp, follow these rules:\n<ol start=\"1\">\n	<li>Wear ear plugs when operating electric tools or heavy machinery, and mowing.</li>\n	<li>Avoid loud music from headphones, while driving, and live concerts.</li>\n	<li>Keep television sets, radios, and alarm clocks at a reasonable noise level.</li>\n	<li>Take breaks from sustained loud noises by moving to a quiet place.</li>\n</ol>\nHearing loss can occur at a sustained noise level of 90-95 decibels. As a general rule of thumb, if you have to raise your voice to be heard, hearing loss can occur. For more information on hearing loss and tinnitus, visit the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001qel0SAE1-vK_U1Syrj1GWk7WwZRzNuEHmf-tPh_0_FmglrmbXW7S3dR0BLFZL2LTF1Q24Z0Iz4rEP4I27dYzMW0UoPfd0NdtY8cUWAjniOk=\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">House Ear Institute</a>.', 'Ringing in the New \'Ears', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1519-revision', '', '', '2013-02-06 17:41:10', '2013-02-06 17:41:10', '', '1519', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1519-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1521', '14', '2013-01-10 17:41:54', '2013-01-10 17:41:54', 'A new year often brings resolutions to frequent the gym, get fit, or lose weight.  Make sure you are properly outfitted for your sport to prevent injuries and maximize your workout. <!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:260.8pt;margin-top:769.5pt;width:91.5pt;height:137.25pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:0;mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right:0;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;mso-position-horizontal:right;\r\n mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical-relative:line\'\r\n o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"https://imgssl.constantcontact.com/ui/stock2/exercise-outfit-woman.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"https://imgssl.constantcontact.com/ui/stock2/exercise-outfit-woman.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"122\" height=\"183\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" /><!--[endif]-->\r\n\r\n<strong>Shoes</strong>- Use only shoes specific to your sport and replace shoes <em>before</em> you feel knee or foot pain. Experts recommend replacing running shoes every 300-400 miles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Safety gear</strong>- Helmets, pads, and high visibility reflective gear are essential to keep you from getting sidelined.\r\n\r\n<strong>Equipment</strong>- Maximizing a workout may require a pedometer, heart rate monitor, or motivating music. Reaching goals may be easier with an online app or progress chart.\r\n\r\n<strong>Clothes</strong>- If exercising in cooler outdoor temps, aim to dress for weather 20 degrees warmer than the actual temperature. Indoors or out, always layer and choose clothes that allow your skin to breathe.\r\n\r\nIf you are shopping around for new workout gear, visit <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001qel0SAE1-vISoqMIuep2QhAhzJzbziJmGMM1Ts8Zk4LWo8e6JpsPplChe4eW1KRACw_kxOTNoesH_tdGALTqjnAeUlxeWBIX-VjBefYBITxuWiwsix7QFW3J5xC_-OxFiHvIXyHUWEoa7txkJVB6rdrFjGWx9F0ncFN592Y5scisXQJC14T1Yg==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">SparkPeople</a>\'s top 6 things to look for. Take care of your fitness equipment and it will take care of you!', 'New Year, New Gear', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-year-new-gear', '', '', '2013-02-06 17:42:31', '2013-02-06 17:42:31', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1521', '0', 'post', '', '0');
