INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1611', '14', '2013-04-11 21:21:05', '2013-04-11 21:21:05', 'Spring marks the annual undertaking to open the windows and deep clean the whole house. Let your cleaning and organizing efforts carry over to the pantry this year as you throw out unwanted food and make space for healthier options.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Medications</span></strong>- Properly dispose of expired prescriptions or over-the-counter medications.</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">When in Doubt</span>- </strong>Throw it out! If you don\'t know how long a food item has been on your shelf, get rid of it.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Junk Food</strong></span>- Read the labels and discard any foods that contain trans fats, artificial dyes, and ingredients you can\'t pronounce.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Don\'t Forget the Fridge</strong></span>- Remove all the items from your refrigerator and freezer and wipe down the shelves. Frozen casseroles should be used within 3 months, and if frozen properly, meat should last up to a year.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen purging your pantry, donate any unused and undamaged items that aren\'t past the expiration date to your local food pantry or homeless shelter. For more food safety information, visit the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001aFzMCgwQ4dWCy4PAvGiYihfKmGaoDAD73BYck0se8Wsvvx3TEFJ4XfNZ6oVd3bG2qgBS_t6cZ8PhEuL1BpT-OpUVx659j6_jw7y2U7S6rjI7Ymko8F5yrgS0igTxFU0wXPfwC5qi-InnjWq3WIsCdyVQy6R_q4Lf\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">USDA fact sheet</a>.', 'Spring Cleaning Out the Cabinets', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'spring-cleaning-out-the-cabinets', '', '', '2013-04-05 21:22:15', '2013-04-05 21:22:15', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1611', '0', 'post', '', '0');
