 a significant amount of vitamin C. This nutrient helps fight colds, boost immunity, and even detoxify the liver. It\'s flavonid and antioxidant compounds have anti-cancer properties against breast, colon, and lung cancer.\n\nAside from culinary uses, lemons can also be used as a natural remedy for cleaning, beauty, and alternative medicine. The acid in lemons can dissolve stains and act as a deodorizer. For a daily boost of the benefits of lemon, add sliced lemon to your ice water. Learn more ways to incorporate fresh lemon into your diet with these <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001tCiLIb5gR23VxNOE_Ei2TbcWxgICRYK7wumgLi9czTug1p_f88HiYgMsHluMOm7jbusKzN3yFAz9Tma4iwd1zbfYC01YhGCxQkhmDa47w8kRsqBhFWTLSLJG1WIVIIoZeuufHsgieUUjyKEUXrSD0kH4uev1-ehlX-tLBFCsBujVrjkZMuy_C9-VeZGxCwK-txNX5K5dYzWmvR-Uw0TmabiH18WfFDtw\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">lemon recipes</a>.', 'From Lemons to Lemonade   ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1667-revision', '', '', '2013-05-01 21:06:46', '2013-05-01 21:06:46', '', '1667', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1667-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1669', '14', '2013-05-28 21:07:19', '2013-05-28 21:07:19', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\ncoordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\nfilled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n<v:formulas>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n</v:formulas>\r\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1031\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\nmargin-left:292.3pt;margin-top:580.5pt;width:117pt;height:118.5pt;z-index:251658240;\r\nmso-wrap-distance-left:2.25pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\nmso-wrap-distance-right:2.25pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\nmso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\nmso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n<v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/486.jpg\"/>\r\n<w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/486.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.486\" width=\"156\" height=\"158\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"3\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Tai Chi is an ancient Chinese form of exercise that is commonly used as a method of stress reduction. This exercise has gained popularity throughout the world as a low-impact exercise that is appropriate for people of all ages and skill levels. Originally developed for self defense, Tai Chi is performed in slow fluid movements so the body remains in motion.\r\n\r\nWhen performed regularly, benefits of Tai Chi can range from better sleep, decreased stress, increased flexibility and stamina, and less joint pain. Most forms of Tai Chi practice a mind-body connection bringing mental clarity and relaxation. Many local gyms offer Tai Chi classes although exercise videos are also readily available. To watch a short clip of Tai Chi, <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001tCiLIb5gR23LoGuDkjQxwQOEDNse02Huh8jlOmmMfTVwDJrc5V77KHnItOIt_rQD313BSEB6MGxS9yFwfR_G6DVZZ20vrd0DbvQJHyyRIwP5PEOCJuLMv9fuLtwwigzWQkJuh3MAgUYpRYMRumtFRjhjlATQR_Mg\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>.', 'Fight Stress with Tai Chi   ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '1669', '', '', '2013-05-01 21:07:53', '2013-05-01 21:07:53', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1669', '0', 'post', '', '0');
