ign=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\n<div><img src=\"https://imgssl.constantcontact.com/letters/images/1101116784221/CONSULTING92G1_TwoWomen_SI0863.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"92\" height=\"92\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"10\" vspace=\"5\" /><a href=\"http://www.lbgh.org/Working_Well_in_Louisian.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> to access the LBGH application page. Please print the <a href=\"http://www.lbgh.org/uploads/Working_Well_in_Louisiana_On_Line_Application.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">application</a> prior to completing on-line. You will need to submit the <a href=\"http://www.lbgh.org/uploads/CHIEF_EXECUTIVE_OFFICER_SIGN_OFF.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">CEO Sign Off</a> sheet. The CEO Sign Off sheet must be submitted to LBGH.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><em>Need help with your application? <a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/contact-us/\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Contact Sterling</a> today! </em></div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table id=\"content_LETTER.BLOCK28\" style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\n<div align=\"center\"><strong>DEADLINE FOR SUBMISSION IS JULY 1, 2013!</strong></div>\n<div align=\"center\"><strong>Winners will be recognized at the 2013 LBGH Annual Luncheon</strong></div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table id=\"content_LETTER.BLOCK30\" style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\n<div align=\"center\">The Working Well in Louisiana Award is co-sponsored by the Louisiana Association of Health Plans and the Louisiana Governor\'s Council on Physical Fitness and Sports.</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Apply Today! Working Well in Louisiana Award', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1690