QYzID-Ki_B2t-6Z0PLRg0_v1m6VoEAldCHMI3yit3KYgzAqQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">2.5-3 cups of vegetables</a> a day and <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk32smKqtDTYWspj1vbMu7ziSBNqhEMyQgApTwisLRkzZfFPp6jLho7x5gS2mjMsWR4mZREXm76g-akLmnj4pHPLJJD60Lbjf9sQBUIM_Iw2LQOU5v2xLkNPAuRUURFw-tA1CHvl_OrZlGEjO6D-LAJBUvR3u87oUyjI=\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">2 cups of fruit</a> a day for most adults. Since getting the recommended serving sizes of produce can be challenging, juicing and smoothies have proven to be an easy and tasty way to consume the vital nutrients and minerals found in fruits and vegetables.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Juicing-</span></strong> A juicing machine extracts juice from whole fruits and vegetables. Seeds and skin are usually removed during the juicing process leaving behind the pulp that contains fiber and other nutrients.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Smoothies-</span></strong> Smoothies can be made in a blender by tossing fruits, vegetables, yogurt, ice, flax or protein powders. Unlike juicing, smoothies keep the pulp and no nutrients are wasted.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nClaims have been made that juicing and smoothies can promote weight loss, prevent cancer, and aid in nutrient absorption. While juicing and smoothies can help you meet the daily requirements, one should not depend solely on a beverage to meet all these needs. It\'s also important to take calorie count into consideration, as it\'s easier to consume more calories when you drink them.  Click here to view <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk31hNOhaCizxLYlBWiuKmiUPy9EbisKJ3EQODeo1V4YruHTAomiBGgEO2c3oPy6HpUzl1DSbGWsBShj2Cmshzbx2pv59Viy5SQqXMs8WXzxGrZ-2fYCVrOlo-ncAJvJVKnEQlWW0GDHFWlprx3GCs7dX\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">juicing and smoothie recipes</a>.', 'The Skinny on Juicing ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-skinny-on-juicing', '', '', '2013-06-12 20:29:32', '2013-06-12 20:29:32', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1709', '0', 'post', '', '0');
