1z21k_7qsk31_azSsDQlzBJHHEdOk13o3oIxruMT0iTKhZRJGxVjqXEzern9MtyTX4X7HVmrBLF920zZ9LYi6vf3slBDoXzllVM1Y0HeEYEVxHvHd2iIIMglC0YKqEaJfhbeFJHOQDUcb6OoohWhYGb6uvuEfzKsn28RdhRs5ytnbWumtCX-7SVDWSIFudgv3\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">10 ways</a> you can celebrate National Running Day:\r\n\r\n1) <strong>Bring a \"runway\" to work</strong>- Pack your sneakers for a lunch time jog with colleagues.\r\n\r\n2) <strong>Change Happy Hour into Running Hour</strong>- Relax over miles instead of cocktails.\r\n\r\n3) <strong>Strike new ground</strong>- Take the road less traveled for new scenery.\r\n\r\n4) <strong>Make running run in the family</strong>- Get the whole clan involved in a jog around the block.\r\n\r\n5)<strong> Choose a running resolution</strong>- Start a new fitness goal!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk33UuS5-1SGKbzchV9IUzhkdoRwYofdvraURIeMvdCYPUar9Z1PHMF29DnLPnVW0JK-wQoPJjB1vSyuBLlKybFkFVwFW9xBZscVriHXvUOBy1h15UXmYhyu0vAFGvxsuPd0tcGrHSGuErA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Join a group run</a> in your city or schedule to host a new meet up in your neighborhood. For more information on National Running Day or to proclaim why you run, visit the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk332rZmLHSfHcEu8JiAxv2a7BW1zEFbFMzxis534FejEW6sjldLc4JXYfMzenYJhSLExq9f_Uk03DXMQVvHvqeucEawCYPWtchAwpVPjRw9t3RNASIfJXAOu\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">National Running Day homepage</a>.', 'Renew Your Resolution for Running', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'renew-your-resolution-for-running', '', '', '2013-06-12 20:30:31', '2013-06-12 20:30:31', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1712', '0', 'post', '', '0');
