rong>Why Zebras Don\'t Get Ulcers</strong></em><strong> by Robert Sapolsky</strong> explains how prolonged stress causes a range of mental and physical conditions. Gain insight on how to control stress responses.</li>\n	<li><em><strong>Twinkie, Deconstructed</strong></em><strong> by Steve Ettlinger</strong> explores the origin, processing, and dangers of common ingredients in our modern food supply.</li>\n	<li><em><strong>Mindless Eating</strong></em><strong> by Brian Wansink</strong> brings insight and awareness to how much we\'re eating and why we eat when we aren\'t hungry. Recognize secret triggers that cause us to overeat.</li>\n	<li><em><strong>In Defense of Food</strong></em><strong> by Michael Pollan</strong> gets back to the basics of nutrition; \"Eat food, not too much, mostly plants.\" If the food-like substances we consume today wouldn\'t be recognized by your great-grandmother, don\'t eat it.</li>\n</ul>\nMany best selling health books offer advice to improve your diet or fitness, but always be aware of sound medical research and ask your physician before starting a new health regimen. To view more books on health and wellness, visit the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk31xfayPS1YGaENEVMwm_zoAyBDqN1DCk-wfEK_1ZNBI3jzv0LhwclOrkghYUejkExQG6JkHzcN5f6M-YJ4GsbXcY_h-Kum2i-ZpjlTuIWKrgfUCPZ7w0iVAg612C9S-u3eNcVRMgBj3i6yVLWoJCl7i4iUJnL49F_FXWiDxTWpcuA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">New York Times Best Sellers</a> list.', 'Worthy Summer Reads', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1715-revision', '', '', '2013-06-12 20:31:10', '2013-06-12 20:31:10', '', '1715', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1715-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1717', '14', '2013-06-21 20:31:41', '2013-06-21 20:31:41', '[caption id=\"attachment_1718\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"150\"]<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Rene-Broussard-2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-1718 \" title=\"Rene Broussard, 2\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Rene-Broussard-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> René Broussard, LPN, Health Coach[/caption]\r\n\r\nA: The month of June plays host to the first day of summer as well as the official start of the hurricane season. While too much sun exposure and dehydration are the big offenders of summer, those aren\'t the only things in need of seasonal preparation.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Allergies</span></strong>- While pollen is the most common summer allergen, we also need to be aware of other seasonal allergens like mold, bug bites and stings, poison ivy, seasonal fruits and sunscreen allergies. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk33beSU-ClBxpHLkUmXr8-n1ltgJvB4Y1mMPLo8N95AnqoeILVUr72QjbQ4dbdschfZAKCmQlPN53qnUSyWuAHREEFJRk48A_z5Nfln-roQN5EuTwG-iqdvima03bVkLgZ-JzVbOtW0yKe7K_-CyjzVV\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">View the national allergy forecast here</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Water Safety</span></strong>- It is advised to have at least one family member trained in lifesaving skills such as First-Aid and <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk33x7kJBHMpuTSGcjNMHNH-IiFWhwd5RDUv2-IaRGvbIJcImlNH7ds4YCK1z-GqWI-5x_iclJo8MrSSPJwyOD1i2OhibBYnxaA009ko5gr4TXIcOV7s_jyLJ4sLoFEe0Svc=\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">CPR/AED</a>. Familiarize yourself with boating safety guidelines and <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk33hk7ioemqyFwCWvX-Bnjz0aLb5AQ9HHTQZTK0K3kgpS_QRUgP6X-4KAy15XFgNfljci56ll1bcB2G2PzzRn-JcS75i7D_qVDRq-G0qKTKsDW-rg-5ABxH6niPFUzkcdHQ4CQypFFtnM_rClTzRHHCX-vTErCqcd1U=\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">nautical charts</a> before operating watercraft.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Natural Disasters</span></strong>- Whether your area is prone to floods, earthquakes, tornadoes, or hurricanes, it\'s important to have procedures in place <em>before</em> an event occurs that can help you \"weather the storm\" and aid in recovery after the event. Print the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk33Zs2Se5wi3oVgERneEu9u2_XZ_2T2LheFlMX60BxTjLWIrnyN1wfRtamT6xGBi9qj-rw1YAHJKWYRTWEZmlZvdOE2IvXVKAUt95w11vNVODkomdC_v6szBWuiV0rgwXBf8mNyScf7ipWe7cZWux-NsW8KOi_P3Tm2QB151zBDgeUJ-a-Z_2XRNsxflLSNb4eMzCgsyPrseHAygcrHQ6vbD\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Red Cross emergency checklist</a> and create a disaster kit including one gallon of water per person per day, non-perishable food, a first aid kit, and important medical and household documents.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMobile phone apps such as <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk31XB3idbjc6NlFLc8WCkNHyRDZfK46nzdoXFxsNV5XlmVk7auNPQcsuAw2Q79_Zkw-qQOK5yB9AChmC8acLBeQLpqUqm_sbdaVZ0mELhYcgvxj7gRw7mAmrcW7PDjs5bbBFX8ELbr76p_2fA6ufS6Troqxg9t2tf8I=\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">recreational boating safety</a> and <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk32DsxYUNtMj3rOZ4PLMZWeDTPJGuGmzHxPNe-pojV1QV8Y2UGeWt932Z7OoN3ynCKRxEtPLD1DnlwzNE0VHYTd-HZzQWMvnIeSzXOtSSmzOb6W_bAbIvZ5X_bC1Zttt1OszSnQOulU_LPyKf7U2OtLZ\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">weather channel app</a> can offer instant information in a time of uncertainty. For additional summer preparedness information, visit the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk30fcVA3dn21_lywRsdo85asZEi0mD_DasUU0WccFt_lz_9RWPFtz2y2IwmLtd3QtvZjEuE_QdHrvjnYGADfvzvto2tD2ihFoooNxAXVUfVG6g==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Red Cross</a>, <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk32xKg6UyDG_YtvFHxlzmUjTCf9v6JWBuydcyUKFfahOV3optv0rdcknhIbKcoLZBjGla4q1upQxXufE6XD_AvpL0G_npFqDA8koEoIGy1y4CsFUQcz4Y6od859c2QHMOXbaoRIXD-Q-kg==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">NOAA</a>, <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk30XCAc7tSf-9h5b5BKqfSAL34WNvmLfTfk_ekz0Mep3SeJH62HCCtBQZlSq8MpoatKp2cbbT_JcmrmjWfITMTDpTuBY4txfY4nMX3zuRmcYsQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Weather Channel</a> or <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001z21k_7qsk30lM5A5xx_Rq7hrFOx91sS9JriAslWgun8ySjJ1_ZFiVyy9SW1JIs1b-ifcd8i8FDXKFugWeVLxUgw-u_2ZD9-f88nZI6s1tmbgxdNRvWv7yZ9d1pKzmK9T66tpIynjYQDNxty3TXSfKA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Pollen.com.</a>', 'Q: \"What tips can you share for summer safety?\"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'q-what-tips-can-you-share-for-summer-safety', '', '', '2013-06-12 20:33:28', '2013-06-12 20:33:28', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1717', '0', 'post', '', '0');
