ractice being in solitude to reflect on your thoughts. Eliminate background noise like the radio or TV. Do light stretches or practice taking deep breaths in silence. Block out time in a quiet area where you can do this each day. If an area indoors doesn\'t allow this practice, take your solitude outside and listen to the quiet sounds of nature. <em><a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001tL1JIB7AncvqUItz-rBYEB4oX_wwkrlljTRJyEZiZM5DxZiskdThVZQLBOF9oPPFMMnRtWUlhWvrZyg8XnY1T8Ex5z0m7Jj5rBbczXP-808TSZblpFqoPsCrws7KfM_kSX6g4-djZbOz6dCo7rZ72ahrHRFvcfzE\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">More</a></em>', 'The Sound of Silence ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-sound-of-silence', '', '', '2013-09-04 21:19:31', '2013-09-04 21:19:31', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1804', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1805', '14', '2013-09-04 21:19:03', '2013-09-04 21:19:03', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\n <v:formulas>\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\n </v:formulas>\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\n margin-left:0;margin-top:495pt;width:174pt;height:114.75pt;z-index:251658240;\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/640.jpg\"/>\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/640.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.640\" width=\"232\" height=\"153\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Silence is a natural remedy for stress. Some noises such as sirens or traffic can cause blood pressure and heart rate to rise. Just 10 minutes of solitude can help lower stress levels and promote better health.\n\nSince silence isn\'t natural, practice being in solitude to reflect on your thoughts. Eliminate background noise like the radio or TV. Do light stretches or practice taking deep breaths in silence. Block out time in a quiet area where you can do this each day. If an area indoors doesn\'t allow this practice, take your solitude outside and listen to the quiet sounds of nature. <em><a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001tL1JIB7AncvqUItz-rBYEB4oX_wwkrlljTRJyEZiZM5DxZiskdThVZQLBOF9oPPFMMnRtWUlhWvrZyg8XnY1T8Ex5z0m7Jj5rBbczXP-808TSZblpFqoPsCrws7KfM_kSX6g4-djZbOz6dCo7rZ72ahrHRFvcfzE\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">More</a></em>', 'The Sound of Silence ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1804-revision', '', '', '2013-09-04 21:19:03', '2013-09-04 21:19:03', '', '1804', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1804-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1806', '14', '2013-09-16 21:19:37', '2013-09-16 21:19:37', '<span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1029\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:274.3pt;margin-top:661.5pt;width:101.25pt;height:151.5pt;\r\n z-index:251658240;mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/639.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/639.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.639\" width=\"135\" height=\"202\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->When you are sick or hurt, it is often hard to decide where you should go to be treated. It\'s important to have an existing relationship with an established physician </span><em style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\">before</em><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\"> you need treatment. New patient waiting lists for general care providers can be weeks if not months driving patients to Urgent Care Clinics or ERs with higher co-pays and out-of-pocket expenses. Emergency room visits should be reserved for life-threatening conditions only.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Primary Care Physician</strong>- Should be seen for annual physicals, health management, general care such as ear aches or sore throat, and prescription medications.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Urgent Care Clinic</strong>- After hours care for those symptoms listed above that require primary care attention.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Emergency Room</strong>- Visit in the event of loss of consciousness, trauma, signs of heart attack or stroke, poisoning, severe allergic reactions, or severe bleeding or vomiting.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you have questions about coverage, co-pays, or in-network providers, contact your HR department or insurance provider.', 'Choosing the Right Level of Care ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'choosing-the-right-level-of-care', '', '', '2013-09-04 21:20:23', '2013-09-04 21:20:23', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1806', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1807', '14', '2013-09-04 21:19:51', '2013-09-04 21:19:51', '&nbsp;\n\nWhen you are sick or hurt, it is often hard to decide where you should go to be treated. It\'s important to have an existing relationship with an established physician <em>before</em> you need treatment. New patient waiting lists for general care providers can be weeks if not months driving patients to Urgent Care Clinics or ERs with higher co-pays and out-of-pocket expenses. Emergency room visits should be reserved for life-threatening conditions only.\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Primary Care Physician</strong>- Should be seen for annual physicals, health management, general care such as ear aches or sore throat, and prescription medications.</li>\n	<li><strong>Urgent Care Clinic</strong>- After hours care for those symptoms listed above that require primary care attention.</li>\n	<li><strong>Emergency Room</strong>- Visit in the event of loss of consciousness, trauma, signs of heart attack or stroke, poisoning, severe allergic reactions, or severe bleeding or vomiting.</li>\n</ul>\nIf you have questions about coverage, co-pays, or in-network providers, contact your HR department or insurance provider.', 'Choosing the Right Level of Care ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1806-revision', '', '', '2013-09-04 21:19:51', '2013-09-04 21:19:51', '', '1806', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1806-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
