INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1843', '14', '2013-11-13 21:44:53', '2013-11-13 21:44:53', '<img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/749.jpg?a=1115151681356\" alt=\"\" width=\"197\" height=\"178\" />\r\n\r\n<em>Did Someone Say Sleep?</em>\r\n\r\nAre you one of the 41 million Americans not getting enough sleep? One in 3 people will suffer from insomnia at some point in their lifetime. To get more out of your shut-eye, limit caffeine and nicotine in the afternoon and evening hours, and avoid large meals before bedtime. Physical activity and stress management techniques will promote sounder sleep.\r\n\r\nThe key to falling asleep quickly and staying asleep is learning how to turn off your mind. Keep paper and pen by your bed to jot down lingering thoughts and tasks. Avoid screens from cell phones, computers, and TV prior to bedtime, and go to bed and wake up at the same time each day. <em><a href=\"http://www.helpguide.org/topics/sleep.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">More</a></em>', 'Getting the Most Out of Your Zz\'s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'getting-the-most-out-of-your-zzs', '', '', '2013-11-13 21:45:04', '2013-11-13 21:45:04', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1843', '0', 'post', '', '0');
