 get help designing your own personal quit plan by <a href=\"http://www.cancer.org/healthy/toolsandcalculators/quizzes/app/smoking-habits-quiz\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">taking this Stop Smoking quiz</a>.\n\nThe annual Great American Smokeout observance encourages smokers to use the date to make a plan to quit, or to plan in advance and quit smoking that day. Smoking harms nearly every organ in the body, and drastically increases the risk for heart disease, COPD, and multiple kinds of cancer.\n\nTelephone quit lines and support groups are other ways to increase your chances for success. Call 1-800-ACS-2345 to find one in your area. <em><a href=\"http://www.cancer.org/healthy/stayawayfromtobacco/greatamericansmokeout/index\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">More</a></em>', 'Quit Smoking. For Good. ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1848-revision', '', '', '2013-11-13 21:47:35', '2013-11-13 21:47:35', '', '1848', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1848-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1850', '14', '2013-11-24 21:48:09', '2013-11-24 21:48:09', '<div>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/roasted-root-vegetables.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-1851\" title=\"roasted root vegetables\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/roasted-root-vegetables-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Add color and nutrition to your menu with these hearty fall flavors. Make it your own by trying combinations of various vegetables, herbs or spices. Toss the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Combine red potatoes, carrots, celery root, rutabaga, onion, parsnips, and garlic.</li>\r\n	<li>Add fresh rosemary and thyme leaves.</li>\r\n	<li>Toss spices and vegetables together and spread over sprayed baking sheet.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>Roast for 30 minutes at 425°F. Pour broth over vegetables and roast an additional 20 minutes until the vegetables are tender.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div><a href=\"http://allrecipes.com/recipe/oven-roasted-root-vegetables/\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Visit AllRecipes Oven Roasted Root Vegetable recipe for complete directions and reviews.</a></div>', 'Recipe of the Month- Roasted Root Vegetables  ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-roasted-root-vegetables', '', '', '2013-11-13 21:56:01', '2013-11-13 21:56:01', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1850', '0', 'post', '', '0');
