gers your emotional eating, and replace eating with a different coping mechanism like a quick walk, yoga, or drinking water.\r\n\r\nEmotional hunger often strikes suddenly. Instead of immediately reaching for comfort food, consider if you are truly hungry, or if you are just craving food in response to emotion.\r\n\r\nBeing mindful of the true hunger sensation takes practice and control. Try drinking water, as hunger is often confused for thirst, or give yourself the apple test. Ask, \"If all I had right now was an apple, would I eat it?\" If the answer is no, identify the emotional need you are trying to satisfy. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001X6b8VibYHSRJSkMGa2g8a5KAfx1e9gLZh6XqHVGjAdf5HarKQKzeXgZC50Hc7j6_OOuAOajDZCRHgOPr4uW0PT7kAfFhmN1Z6qGmrLKP0xQgxmVnIN9MeoXRWO4zWAS2aq5KhNjOUPAht7oUHLTnotadPkOpAfU-QYjaPLN9dQgX87C4CD14URiS_Js7_aax\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Overcoming Emotional Eating', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1901-revision-2', '', '', '2014-01-08 21:06:54', '2014-01-08 21:06:54', '', '1901', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1901-revision-2/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1904', '14', '2014-01-16 21:07:05', '2014-01-16 21:07:05', '<strong>Eating Clean in Twenty-Fourteen</strong>\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:264.95pt;margin-top:725.75pt;width:138pt;height:96.75pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/823.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/823.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.823\" width=\"184\" height=\"129\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->The focus of clean eating is not to lose weight, but rather to improve the diet by avoiding packaged foods that are processed with chemicals, fillers, and food dyes. Clean eating includes nutrient-dense foods grown out of the ground in the form of whole grains, legumes, seeds, nuts, and produce (organic when possible). Include healthy fats and lean meats in your clean diet, and stay hydrated with filtered water.\r\n\r\nWork toward a clean diet by slowly freeing your cabinets of center-isle refined foods. Learn to read food labels and avoid ingredients you can\'t pronounce. Generally speaking, the shorter an ingredient list is, the better. Chemically processed ingredients can numb the taste buds to the flavor of healthy clean foods, so it might take a few tries before your palate is refined to the taste of vegetables! <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001X6b8VibYHSQoMD4Li-wLGhpwV1amoXTNY07Va2a2KWRereqmrx4F1xjoP2Mn8CMjQwgTGDdLZYNeXc5R1VHhYQac427UpgVPlb2qH518NI3_DloEaXGYFicPrZ8HRTpH5kNPnVF8O5q4waWLm_LVUg==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Eating Clean in Twenty-Fourteen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'eating-clean-in-twenty-fourteen', '', '', '2014-01-08 21:07:46', '2014-01-08 21:07:46', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1904', '0', 'post', '', '0');
