rm of whole grains, legumes, seeds, nuts, and produce (organic when possible). Include healthy fats and lean meats in your clean diet, and stay hydrated with filtered water.\n\nWork toward a clean diet by slowly freeing your cabinets of center-isle refined foods. Learn to read food labels and avoid ingredients you can\'t pronounce. Generally speaking, the shorter an ingredient list is, the better. Chemically processed ingredients can numb the taste buds to the flavor of healthy clean foods, so it might take a few tries before your palate is refined to the taste of vegetables! <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001X6b8VibYHSQoMD4Li-wLGhpwV1amoXTNY07Va2a2KWRereqmrx4F1xjoP2Mn8CMjQwgTGDdLZYNeXc5R1VHhYQac427UpgVPlb2qH518NI3_DloEaXGYFicPrZ8HRTpH5kNPnVF8O5q4waWLm_LVUg==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Eating Clean in Twenty-Fourteen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1904-revision', '', '', '2014-01-08 21:07:28', '2014-01-08 21:07:28', '', '1904', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1904-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1906', '14', '2014-01-22 21:07:53', '2014-01-22 21:07:53', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1029\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:0;margin-top:918.65pt;width:129pt;height:130.5pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/817.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/817.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.817\" width=\"172\" height=\"174\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Choosing clothes and layering them properly are keys to keeping comfortable while exercising outdoors, especially in cold temperatures. Adding or removing layers as needed will help you stay warm and dry while staying active.\r\n\r\n<strong>Base Layer: </strong>This layer, closest to your skin, should wick moisture away from your body and into the air or outer layer where it can evaporate. The best base layer materials are lightweight synthetics like polypropylene and polyester.\r\n\r\n<strong>Mid-Layer: </strong>This insulating layer helps to take moisture away from the base layer. Wool and synthetics, such as fleece, work well. This layer should be snug but not constricting. Features such as full-length front zippers allow for venting.\r\n\r\n<strong>Outer Layer: </strong>This layer protects you from the elements. When it\'s dry outside, go for a lightweight soft shell that provides warmth, breathability, and wind resistance. If the conditions are wet, make sure your outer layer is both breathable and waterproof. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001X6b8VibYHSQbdkNuUPNciY9ASlJN8GJXSxQ-xQp4E0e48CYkRmLE-1JcoiS0l55U-k7xVHSahioJ4WPl8fuS4ctSs3_XPnxg3F2yU8XsWuryf6v23_J0cjaz0qg7wqK_6mgIeQzBNiAzwJOearztKzSsQl-K-fm5mZyL0bH5HCsp_yiN6kLWue6QjdTlLqysIaJUUeF4z3JtUrGliRP6ujaEEjM-c4C_\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Bundled Up for Outdoor Fitness ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bundled-up-for-outdoor-fitness', '', '', '2014-01-08 21:08:34', '2014-01-08 21:08:34', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1906', '0', 'post', '', '0');
