INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1913', '14', '2014-01-16 20:44:38', '2014-01-16 20:44:38', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Allen-Torres.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1914\" title=\"Allen Torres\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Allen-Torres-300x270.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"270\" /></a>Allen started his journey toward better health by enrolling in Sterling’s Calling it Quits Tobacco Cessation program. Allen’s vow to change came after his father passed away from a sudden heart attack and his mother was diagnosed with lung cancer. The Calling it Quits 8-week program encouraged Allen to evaluate when and why he smokes, rearrange his environment to overcome barriers and urges, and set a quit date.\r\n\r\nAs a smoker of nearly 20 years, Allen had tried to quit before and gained a significant amount of weight. Determined to avoid weight gain this time, Allen started a weight loss/diet plan the same week he quit smoking. He began eating breakfast by replacing his morning cigarette with an apple. Allen exchanged caffeinated energy drinks with protein shakes and bars and began to feel in control of his environment. With the money he saved from quitting smoking, Allen purchased a treadmill and began walking 30 minutes twice a day and he joined a running club.\r\n\r\nToward the end of the program, Allen chose to get a Vertical Sleeve  procedure. In the 7 weeks since his procedure, Allen has lost 70lbs! He remains smoke free and has plans to complete his<strong> </strong>first 5k in March and 10k race in April!<strong> </strong>Allen admits the journey hasn’t always been easy.<strong> </strong>“The first thing I had to do to turn a negative into a positive was to change my attitude. My commitment to changing my health started with my attitude, my determination, and my courage to succeed at obtaining my goals. I never ever gave up when others said I couldn’t do it,” he says.\r\n\r\nCongratulations on the substantial change to your health and the milestones you achieved along the way!', 'Success Starts with Commitment', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'success-starts-with-commitment', '', '', '2014-01-16 20:54:54', '2014-01-16 20:54:54', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1913', '0', 'post', '', '0');
