ck. Upper body discomfort and shortness of breath are also common symptoms. If you think you or someone around you is experiencing a heart attack, follow these steps:\r\n<ol start=\"1\">\r\n	<li>Contact 9-1-1</li>\r\n	<li>Push hard and fast in the center of the chest to the beat of \'Stayin\' Alive\'</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nYou don\'t have to be certified in CPR/AED to save a life. Simply providing chest compressions to someone in cardiac arrest is a safe and effective way for a bystander to double or triple a person\'s chances of survival. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001kCurY-oSC7Z7Syub2HDvhW5MXYQJobYCsSyBVP6Cy36KwvKWC7yVWPWjnkHhwKaLUN5XIdtuQ5rC0UlWFLoQ42XSVokiUbrDKPviGkSML4jaWpHGGRXxJ1JRgJO1zcygmHiYz11NMY7kbREJzO1_C2BLFEZZaj76_Js5qIyc7NkM_3J8JbRIzLElEAFW5uC_XAK1-AqXLYU5QSM1DR15iXBlTQadFeUo\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Save a Life with Hands-Only CPR', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1926-revision-2', '', '', '2014-02-06 22:20:53', '2014-02-06 22:20:53', '', '1926', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1926-revision-2/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1929', '14', '2014-02-13 22:21:03', '2014-02-13 22:21:03', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:311.05pt;margin-top:666.75pt;width:138pt;height:69pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/846.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/846.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.846\" width=\"184\" height=\"92\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Being inactive nearly doubles your risk of developing heart disease. Aim for at least 2 hours and 30 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic activity each week to reap these benefits:\r\n<ol start=\"1\">\r\n	<li>Aerobic activities like brisk walking or jogging can lower blood pressure 5 to 10 mmHg. That translates into a 10 to 20% reduction in heart attack risk.</li>\r\n	<li>Smokers who become physically active are more likely to stop smoking - or at least smoke less.</li>\r\n	<li>Exercise helps control blood sugar levels and can reduce the heart-related complications linked to diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Physical activity can increase HDL (good cholesterol) and decrease LDL (bad cholesterol).</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Calories burned by regular activity help control weight and prevent obesity</span></li>\r\n</ol>', 'Five Ways Physical Activity Lowers Your Risk for Heart Disease', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'five-ways-physical-activity-lowers-your-risk-for-heart-disease', '', '', '2014-02-06 22:21:37', '2014-02-06 22:21:37', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1929', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1930', '14', '2014-02-06 22:21:14', '2014-02-06 22:21:14', 'Being inactive nearly doubles your risk of developing heart disease. Aim for at least 2 hours and 30 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic activity each week to reap these benefits:\n<ol start=\"1\">\n	<li>Aerobic activities like brisk walking or jogging can lower blood pressure 5 to 10 mmHg. That translates into a 10 to 20% reduction in heart attack risk.</li>\n	<li>Smokers who become physically active are more likely to stop smoking - or at least smoke less.</li>\n	<li>Exercise helps control blood sugar levels and can reduce the heart-related complications linked to diabetes.</li>\n	<li>Physical activity can increase HDL (good cholesterol) and decrease LDL (bad cholesterol).</li>\n</ol>\nCalories burned by regular activity help control weight and prevent obesity', 'Five Ways Physical Activity Lowers Your Risk for Heart Disease', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1929-revision', '', '', '2014-02-06 22:21:14', '2014-02-06 22:21:14', '', '1929', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1929-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1931', '14', '2014-02-16 22:21:46', '2014-02-16 22:21:46', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1029\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:0;margin-top:844.5pt;width:129pt;height:84.75pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/844.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/844.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.844\" width=\"172\" height=\"113\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Stiff and sore? Roll away your muscle aches with a foam roller! These inexpensive foam tubes break up fibrous tissue and increase circulation to the treated area relieving muscle tension and pain right away. Rolling also helps with range of motion and injury prevention.\r\n\r\nUse a foam roller after a workout or incorporate it into your daily stretching routine. Just 10-15 minutes of rolling can target all troublesome areas including hip flexors, IT band, hamstrings, calves and back. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001kCurY-oSC7ZeD7_IqQfCMW4DleooIjPb39eBtfITLzTpYkaJGK29SBiTyaCZzxJGHyj1pXdn_FjgXJsqjsGi2PrNl-bzC3G8NZ7VnrP2pYxQOhn4IFEA8c7rtay8UiA5AqqtrEQodzOh3inup0EKhg==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Roll Away Soreness', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'roll-away-soreness', '', '', '2014-02-06 22:22:21', '2014-02-06 22:22:21', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1931', '0', 'post', '', '0');
