INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1933', '14', '2014-02-22 22:22:31', '2014-02-22 22:22:31', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/quinoa-and-black-beans.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-1934\" title=\"quinoa and black beans\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/quinoa-and-black-beans.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /></a>Quinoa (pronounced \"keen-wah\") is a nutrient-rich whole grain known for its protein, fiber, and iron. Add quinoa to your menu this month by pairing it with black beans:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Saute onion and garlic in saucepan until lightly browned.</li>\r\n	<li>Mix quinoa into the saucepan and cover with broth. Season with cumin, cayenne pepper, salt and pepper.</li>\r\n	<li>Bring mixture to boil, cover, reduce heat and simmer.</li>\r\n	<li>Stir frozen corn into the saucepan and continue to simmer. Mix in black beans and cilantro.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor the complete list of ingredients and directions, view this <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001kCurY-oSC7YB94I4OZZixgt9Z9W6Qbtde8YBhBLehn7_b1hWucMoTDGP91C8Y5scyxc8CBM2I6Tg-JKTf78DVyR4AMU8kbBii5DC_aoFZioZnq1KXA7h0QNakcI1QwcIewFKJ0YK-7t_VTAM6OrDgpfSal38R21h\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Quinoa and Black Bean recipe from AllRecipes.com</a>. Try your own variation of the recipe by including different vegetables or experiment with red, black, or white varieties of quinoa.', 'Recipe of the Month- Quinoa and Black Beans ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-quinoa-and-black-beans', '', '', '2014-02-06 22:23:26', '2014-02-06 22:23:26', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1933', '0', 'post', '', '0');
