health coaching.  Requires excellent presentation skills, interpersonal communication, and computer proficiency.  Serious and qualified inquires only. Submit cover letter, resume, and references.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Fitness Expert</strong></span>- Must be proficient at conducting step test and sit-and-reach, and knowledgeable with other general health and fitness information. Ability to take manual blood pressure is preferred. Early mornings and local travel throughout Lafourche and Terrebonne Parish required. Please submit resume and references below.\r\n\r\n[gravityform id=\"1\" name=\"Careers\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"]', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-19 20:51:27', '2014-03-19 20:51:27', '', '8', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/8-revision-25/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
