 that trigger your symptoms, your doctor can perform a quick and accurate skin test that identifies your allergens.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li>Be cautious of pets that bring pollen inside with them.</li>\n	<li>Avoid the outdoors in the morning when pollen counts are the highest.</li>\n	<li>Keep windows and doors shut in the home and cars.</li>\n	<li>Stay ahead of allergies by beginning an over-the-counter allergy regimen 1-2 weeks before the pollen season begins.</li>\n</ul>\nRecognizing and avoiding allergens in asthmatics can prevent asthma attacks triggered from allergies. If you see early signs of an asthma attack when pollen counts are high, seek treatment as soon as possible to avoid a severe asthma attack. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001_hssVjiVfu3cgzF7pOZtxB2OpzMfzqqmBnFGbSg6Hij07Qxzy2A-KkbReuDQ3rIxbHLKEyHX3o9Oumy71In6DMEUAhuyMjzbMJr6kCahYlgKObHH82Opb24wV0x2eL2NqYP52QHihjeubIerHkKtwA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Controlling Allergies and Asthma Attacks ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1962-revision', '', '', '2014-04-09 19:44:33', '2014-04-09 19:44:33', '', '1962', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/1962-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1964', '14', '2014-04-09 19:45:47', '2014-04-09 19:45:47', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1032\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:0;margin-top:537.75pt;width:118.5pt;height:93pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"https://origin.ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/899.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"https://origin.ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/899.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.899\" width=\"158\" height=\"124\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->As chronic diseases reach epidemic proportions, so do pharmaceuticals and medication. Much of today\'s food is derived from processed foods that lack enzymes and nutrients necessary for fighting disease and boosting immunity. The foods you consume become your body. Whole, organic, and unprocessed foods can be the medicine required to prevent and treat illnesses.\r\n\r\n<strong style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Medicine is not healthcare. Food is healthcare. Medicine is sickcare.   </strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">-Wendell Barry, Author</span>\r\n\r\nModern-day diets are causing us to be over-fed but under-nourished. Replacing high-sugar, high-fat foods with antioxidant rich fruits, vegetables, and whole grains can offer the anti-inflammatory compounds and nutrients for optimal health. Replace your packaged foods with a variety of disease fighting whole foods. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001_hssVjiVfu3cgzF7pOZtxB2OpzMfzqqmBnFGbSg6Hij07Qxzy2A-KkbReuDQ3rIxbHLKEyHX3o9Oumy71In6DMEUAhuyMjzbXZbI64TMWvgPA02-VpzyeiQjwE331lZlVFHlH0hSOqiFI0TCp5PwRa3CNF6reVeYa3YFpVJx4B0kuklwKtgpbw==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Let Food Be Your Medicine', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'let-food-be-your-medicine', '', '', '2014-04-09 19:45:47', '2014-04-09 19:45:47', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1964', '0', 'post', '', '0');
