INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('1998', '14', '2014-05-16 18:55:54', '2014-05-16 18:55:54', '<span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\ncoordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\nfilled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n<v:formulas>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n</v:formulas>\r\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\nmargin-left:326.8pt;margin-top:745.5pt;width:153.75pt;height:105.75pt;\r\nz-index:251658240;mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\nmso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\nmso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\nmso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n<v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/909.jpg\"/>\r\n<w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/909.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.909\" width=\"205\" height=\"141\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->High-Density Lipoprotein, or HDL, is better known as your \"good\" cholesterol. This particle scavenges out LDL, or \"bad\" cholesterol, and shuttles it back to the liver so it doesn\'t build up in the blood stream. Too little HDL can cause an imbalance in LDL, increasing the risk for heart disease. Although a portion of HDL levels are genetically determined, heart healthy choices can significantly impact your good cholesterol:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Exercise</strong>- The best way to increase HDL is to exercise consistently.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Healthy Fats</strong>- Omega 3s found in salmon, flax seed, fish oil, olive oil, and avocados can increase HDL levels.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>If you smoke, quit-</strong> Tobacco smoke lowers HDL.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA good HDL cholesterol level that provides protection against heart disease should be greater than 60mg/dL. Alternatively, an HDL result lower than 40mg/dL places you at higher risk for heart disease. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001Ywe8N9ZzTwJwG0to7lzynpydEQt00js0Oa88RXahARubKFr932nyQwtS9xLmjCE0xmFQ4oF0ymHzPNSA_20lIJTpHdh3NecllRlCAbD7w6tsAKbnxRQyRVQ17tKcoQ6uTz3uq4QHluqkX6RzJSPj-AB5YzlICrR3RDam0TfG6PXv3T6h-KgRVYmNJpuU44Ot5mBbcjrQH1c_yXXNLJqUrur01Z9gzq_fmMEj4VmCa9K9tLPog4Pc7l_n7N5zh4at&amp;c=AeyPheMxmNwwU9wiONArMgcpmTzz69pVIwDHHMKlhLO3eOK0LxsRLw==&amp;ch=9VhzzZMODbeFIBBJg_2DGfFC6iGXIuQ--FP8cpzEO67TozoWNwN7BA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Heart Healthy Choices for Better HDL', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'heart-healthy-choices-for-better-hdl', '', '', '2014-05-08 18:56:42', '2014-05-08 18:56:42', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=1998', '0', 'post', '', '0');
