 feel thirsty.</li>\n	<li>Reduce stress by taking breaks to breathe deeply and stretch.</li>\n	<li>Identify food triggers that may cause headaches including aged cheeses, red wine, and dried fruits.</li>\n	<li>Maintain a sleep schedule that allows optimal rest by going to bed and waking up at the same time every day, even on days off.</li>\n	<li>Limit caffeine and nicotine as both cause headaches and lead to dependency.</li>\n</ul>\nTaking good care of yourself by exercising consistently and not skipping meals can also prevent headaches. If your headaches are severe or interfere with daily activities, talk to your doctor about underlying issues or taking over-the-counter or prescription medication. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0018BxFD73nH2sMuT5Sqi0JD5GHovIi3AMZ1mLmOyraUghOOTc-J7Ryavd7HErQIK2CK0RSlIWKZzT5hQN5UxxmAiKrhZ9Gvq95Cc_Xbiv7IE-_KyGhtestqnRU7_TwrJ01odCBnAvI7A1TBOseziml7tdGnqRQEaHSFYoOTeLZImGZh8pMPRxEPOGREQoPlNl0wC6pfhKTuuiA7tKPbeYddHE7_wYYaaLIbTBcxOjiFsmHHtXnodPM3o6-B78IzjpOXJxyJRX0trlUjVrIQVqa0A==&amp;c=3OCuyNg9dPUZ5c5tba2NwtrfuYQgGKPb2f8FIu9Ycy3440zzpdI_JA==&amp;ch=sNAvtMW6cR7Jiifwc9B7mTsIyqTdshBrGsu6f3oWjDQI8bVVgOCUOw==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Help for Headaches', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2029-revision', '', '', '2014-06-11 19:05:10', '2014-06-11 19:05:10', '', '2029', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2029-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
