 these steps:\r\n\r\n1. <strong>T</strong>rain gradually by adding days of rest in between. Avoid over-training and repetitive overuse from jobs or sports.\r\n\r\n2. <strong>L</strong>ose excess weight. Every pound of body weight adds 5 pounds of extra stress on the joint.\r\n\r\n3. <strong>C</strong>ondition knees by strengthening hips, glutes, and quads. Use machine weights or resistance bands to perform 3 sets of 8-10 repetitions of exercises including knee extensions, leg lifts, squats, and lunges.\r\n\r\nAging and osteoarthritis can increase chances of knee problems. If you experience serious persistent pain that limits your mobility, talk to a doctor or orthopedic specialist.  <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0018BxFD73nH2sMuT5Sqi0JD5GHovIi3AMZ1mLmOyraUghOOTc-J7RyaiGxg4Oc_Y8xPYTlb4QYMCpVFhouBR5Qia5iwAQnbZj-R9eJr2zK4iEDYYjy5NGkPwAOv62MgQWPclF_21reJd-5p9x9J47QAqUeelnZFydEDQMNRfdKEOC3kwl3pEwLfxz-AtUwQtUjxP905KT7V1FrC3bNcXkbGH5rHzZ_pjmLRwX6Bvrqm2xvyAO9o48Yj06s5IzvAujwqWmHiHQvk7zA8K0TGuL_IEeXjsiOtk7SCfAJJ9LD40c=&amp;c=3OCuyNg9dPUZ5c5tba2NwtrfuYQgGKPb2f8FIu9Ycy3440zzpdI_JA==&amp;ch=sNAvtMW6cR7Jiifwc9B7mTsIyqTdshBrGsu6f3oWjDQI8bVVgOCUOw==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Give Your Knees a Little TLC', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'give-your-knees-a-little-tlc', '', '', '2014-06-11 19:06:24', '2014-06-11 19:06:24', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2031', '0', 'post', '', '0');
