s condition, thyroid problems can affect men as well.\r\n\r\nWhen the thyroid malfunctions, it secretes too much or too little hormone. An under-active thyroid, or hypothyroidism, can cause constant fatigue, poor mental focus, and unexplained weight gain. Conversely, an over-active thyroid, or hyperthyroidism, can cause heart palpitations, weight loss, perspiration at rest, and nervousness. Lumps on the thyroid, also known as nodules, or an enlarged thyroid can indicate a problem with the gland. Give yourself a <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001VOpxTRrKs6wv0vEMJeDCao1vG6r3CubnDbE3xY3TTeaE6PAdxEPxNbimSTc8qmUcpPw_K8mKO0K7I-BR-GBNVaMyOBg6G2k_edTbsDlKDk-ZWkyKYwI1X3w6FGQz673CM7uuJheXuJ_ufZAGUcBdm0T14WFBLgB2F_lHRAD4ROFmibLJDmXLbFrHIibAIVovvqu6JgGoL9w=&amp;c=n0lHuwNSFUvafKGWQk6bg7qT_vcINbxG2MABEU1kGiPWPF78mny1fw==&amp;ch=carGuHigQ4jT9_8Vn1-PB8e7i0BmDi-fe9TxToN09rBWiaklVupmYA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">neck check</a> and talk to your doctor if you have symptoms of a thyroid disorder. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001VOpxTRrKs6wv0vEMJeDCao1vG6r3CubnDbE3xY3TTeaE6PAdxEPxNbimSTc8qmUcfawJrd_JHpntRNiRHF9GXSX92if4clbG_YIceXtjWtMbLGEU854wam7p9oMZ9_rhVJiv_S0zZx_UEymcZCPSThfgaJAjrQ84rvTHCqaHhjSSW4LclrSXkpvYRL9h8rCDIe5M5mvvXfBABBQ6cUmjnw==&amp;c=n0lHuwNSFUvafKGWQk6bg7qT_vcINbxG2MABEU1kGiPWPF78mny1fw==&amp;ch=carGuHigQ4jT9_8Vn1-PB8e7i0BmDi-fe9TxToN09rBWiaklVupmYA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Time For Your Neck Check', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'time-for-your-neck-check', '', '', '2014-07-09 19:27:01', '2014-07-09 19:27:01', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2046', '0', 'post', '', '0');
