s seem less tiring.\r\n\r\nThe weight loss benefits of stair climbing can significantly add up as well. Taking the stairs burns twice as many calories as walking. A 150 pound person burns about 10 calories per minute climbing stairs, while riding an elevator burns about 1 calorie a minute. While these numbers are nearly negligible in this example, climbing two flights of stairs daily could result in a weight loss of 6 pounds in a year!\r\n\r\nThe CDC recommends adults get at least 2 hours and 30 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic activity each week. Ten minute intervals of activity count toward that total, so start stepping! <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001mqpT30LjS0PvZXYpyrESPw8ALO1tSwDbFYVu4wxvn-eUH0A4E5kjZmrClFo9-anNSDR76CuLkGJgDR6nKoU6O1DWP8gfslkb-k3lT4v_iUqr5drsPHEeilrbd9dji81MQ5xRZ2kthUyHEYIve8tbB4uQm9wdVSPzZK5LOYbspdZZCcKi3F570LMOz6KIxuCDo6IWQYoT_Ob9LvsQc7KEHsJoH4fYTJ17gZfH3Aj-UPQ=&amp;c=Y6so3ePEoYCLKwKzG_9oihVFb0oHY07yf_5jxnN7Z9yVFywcCBnFmA==&amp;ch=FQMVJ-rUubFxc7mO267pJ9SlnOnW2h_dB_lJkMYLg2H-lrBSsD-fdQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Stairway to Health', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'stairway-to-health', '', '', '2014-09-04 20:34:18', '2014-09-04 20:34:18', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2082', '0', 'post', '', '0');
