0.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001mqpT30LjS0PvZXYpyrESPw8ALO1tSwDbFYVu4wxvn-eUH0A4E5kjZmrClFo9-anNgQra-eOgyYTZ0nQMYpGC6wE_NUMC6_oE3GhXOKEMkTaFuBDl2TPhpsqN-PbFFgP3tjixB_KokSVz5dLI6Begx7U3Ncr95uaX4IdO8gB6lxiV0rQ0NR9G4U5pd4g42IWFYPNnaA-fBqNmmeN1zDfF44It3GFNYlbcLSUndanu46nJ_xTL3BiySg==&amp;c=Y6so3ePEoYCLKwKzG_9oihVFb0oHY07yf_5jxnN7Z9yVFywcCBnFmA==&amp;ch=FQMVJ-rUubFxc7mO267pJ9SlnOnW2h_dB_lJkMYLg2H-lrBSsD-fdQ==\" target=\"&quot;_blank&quot;\"><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/1040.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1040\" width=\"167\" height=\"167\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /></a><!--[endif]-->Pizza night just got a makeover! This fun twist on fruit pizza uses watermelon slices as the base and fresh fruit toppings for color and nutrition.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut a large round watermelon into 1\" thick slices.</li>\r\n	<li>Top watermelon rounds with fruit slices of your choice. Try kiwi, berries, bananas and peaches.</li>\r\n	<li>Sprinkle with shredded coconut, almond slivers, or dark chocolate chips.</li>\r\n	<li>Segment into wedges and enjoy!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere is no right or wrong way to make your own version, so have fun experimenting!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001mqpT30LjS0PvZXYpyrESPw8ALO1tSwDbFYVu4wxvn-eUH0A4E5kjZmrClFo9-anNgQra-eOgyYTZ0nQMYpGC6wE_NUMC6_oE3GhXOKEMkTaFuBDl2TPhpsqN-PbFFgP3tjixB_KokSVz5dLI6Begx7U3Ncr95uaX4IdO8gB6lxiV0rQ0NR9G4U5pd4g42IWFYPNnaA-fBqNmmeN1zDfF44It3GFNYlbcLSUndanu46nJ_xTL3BiySg==&amp;c=Y6so3ePEoYCLKwKzG_9oihVFb0oHY07yf_5jxnN7Z9yVFywcCBnFmA==&amp;ch=FQMVJ-rUubFxc7mO267pJ9SlnOnW2h_dB_lJkMYLg2H-lrBSsD-fdQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Click here to get the recipe from Daily Creative Ideas.</em></a>', 'Recipe of the Month- Watermelon Pizza', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-watermelon-pizza', '', '', '2014-09-04 20:35:34', '2014-09-04 20:35:34', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2084', '0', 'post', '', '0');
