mportant thing you can do to keep from getting sick.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Eating immune boosting foods</strong> like garlic, vitamin C, vitamin D, echinacea, and zinc not only reduce the susceptibility of colds, but can reduce the severity of them.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Loading up on probiotics</strong> found in yogurt and kefir can protect against respiratory illnesses and fight infection.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Managing stress</strong> reduces the duration of colds. Chronic stress disrupts the body\'s ability to fight off illnesses.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Getting adequate sleep</strong> helps the body respond to infections.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo respect others, please stay home if you are sick to prevent the further spread of germs. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001flEtcTDLdOZcCASGWG2VlPx97V89fa9a8Y9fj5vfE-95eQU-99N_cxRgdmthzEcKPfph-LXLBzJghScbZbYNsT4WhrxBFHa-BjDS_MAXyDmceFMoZv-H9qGia6nyAnJ6_H6PaXcQwU2PSanXWTq3219q8KWI9wuyi-b8epWyc1kMMOSB_260zAeryVfNGOSoWxeNhAPmvuRHg6LHB8HrMaWXInXPF0iRZb7FLEbN8_Cw_WJLeAwn7zcuRW8EC8P2&amp;c=BQa7v_ihdbetQOubnidRuCxNBdY5cOYTZ-bKQPFWeEm78-8UCQbUZg==&amp;ch=ApL6b9g-7RJ41hLsF2jiTI6_uerR0NpJcT16c8eaiIyrSi1JNj6MBA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Building a Strong Line of Defense', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'building-a-strong-line-of-defense', '', '', '2014-10-09 16:04:36', '2014-10-09 16:04:36', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2094', '0', 'post', '', '0');
