y objects. Kettle bell design allows transitions from one exercise to the next without needing to readjust positions, resulting in greater calorie burn in less time.\r\n\r\nA study by the ACE determined that kettle bell exercises are an efficient way to combine both cardiovascular and strength training in one short session, eliminating the need to split time between cardio machines and weights. Most kettle bell exercises engage multiple muscle groups for a full-body workout that can burn up to 20 calories in a minute. Proper form is essential to prevent injury. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001flEtcTDLdOZcCASGWG2VlPx97V89fa9a8Y9fj5vfE-95eQU-99N_cxRgdmthzEcKvoLmAoBAj1_9wK7E_K2MK7vup8ZRpVXh9pKhcw5cdyjyCU6ImiRHTUo6uYe6NdDwiJXr27ZHNv3Vd2WEoypoHoJLMbGK8bmspZ0vNYshCJw14mqdhvqNBNbyMDVwhyQX2S8qr12M4XmwKYvYeUL3ihseBw5Ub6c2U-vQfWRQBrmzjwfXbX_k8DFnbGEM5AIOTTjh7dtA3P9xer53KoOXAZ4hYwgKkGhB&amp;c=BQa7v_ihdbetQOubnidRuCxNBdY5cOYTZ-bKQPFWeEm78-8UCQbUZg==&amp;ch=ApL6b9g-7RJ41hLsF2jiTI6_uerR0NpJcT16c8eaiIyrSi1JNj6MBA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The Kettle Bells Are Calling', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-kettle-bells-are-calling', '', '', '2014-10-09 16:10:23', '2014-10-09 16:10:23', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2102', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2103', '14', '2014-10-09 16:10:07', '2014-10-09 16:10:07', 'Amp up your functional fitness by including kettle bell exercises in your workout. These weighted orbs with handles are advantageous over dumbbells because the center of gravity shifts while lifting them, in the same way you would lift everyday objects. Kettle bell design allows transitions from one exercise to the next without needing to readjust positions, resulting in greater calorie burn in less time.\n\nA study by the ACE determined that kettle bell exercises are an efficient way to combine both cardiovascular and strength training in one short session, eliminating the need to split time between cardio machines and weights. Most kettle bell exercises engage multiple muscle groups for a full-body workout that can burn up to 20 calories in a minute. Proper form is essential to prevent injury. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001flEtcTDLdOZcCASGWG2VlPx97V89fa9a8Y9fj5vfE-95eQU-99N_cxRgdmthzEcKvoLmAoBAj1_9wK7E_K2MK7vup8ZRpVXh9pKhcw5cdyjyCU6ImiRHTUo6uYe6NdDwiJXr27ZHNv3Vd2WEoypoHoJLMbGK8bmspZ0vNYshCJw14mqdhvqNBNbyMDVwhyQX2S8qr12M4XmwKYvYeUL3ihseBw5Ub6c2U-vQfWRQBrmzjwfXbX_k8DFnbGEM5AIOTTjh7dtA3P9xer53KoOXAZ4hYwgKkGhB&amp;c=BQa7v_ihdbetQOubnidRuCxNBdY5cOYTZ-bKQPFWeEm78-8UCQbUZg==&amp;ch=ApL6b9g-7RJ41hLsF2jiTI6_uerR0NpJcT16c8eaiIyrSi1JNj6MBA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', '', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2102-revision', '', '', '2014-10-09 16:10:07', '2014-10-09 16:10:07', '', '2102', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2102-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
