=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001flEtcTDLdOZcCASGWG2VlPx97V89fa9a8Y9fj5vfE-95eQU-99N_c0Dz090O3lTX6KIUgdgjTSI_tr4wOCnqDrr8TM72jKSp5tGQhPCECQ-FtRyLrt1_gS3uLJq1BLxDCkKuZz9seKR8fya6NMvoWi8Tns06jrxzeyzjvU33VWago6ZmiMf7cWkdf_hT9O5d8b6UIeC46vfom9lHwEObb2iI55T71J5c&amp;c=BQa7v_ihdbetQOubnidRuCxNBdY5cOYTZ-bKQPFWeEm78-8UCQbUZg==&amp;ch=ApL6b9g-7RJ41hLsF2jiTI6_uerR0NpJcT16c8eaiIyrSi1JNj6MBA==\" target=\"&quot;_blank&quot;\"><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/1080.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1080\" width=\"204\" height=\"128\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /></a><!--[endif]-->What\'s not to love about these simple, quick, and healthy baked sweet potato fries?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Slice 4 medium sweet potatoes into thin strips.</li>\r\n	<li>Toss potatoes in a large bowl with canola or olive oil.</li>\r\n	<li>Sprinkle salt and pepper and continue to toss until coated.</li>\r\n	<li>Spread potatoes evenly on cookie sheets.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCook sweet potato fries in a 450° preheated oven turning fries halfway through cooking. Cook until crisp, about 35 minutes. Flavor to your liking by trying cajun spices, cinnamon, or rosemary and thyme.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001flEtcTDLdOZcCASGWG2VlPx97V89fa9a8Y9fj5vfE-95eQU-99N_c0Dz090O3lTX6KIUgdgjTSI_tr4wOCnqDrr8TM72jKSp5tGQhPCECQ-FtRyLrt1_gS3uLJq1BLxDCkKuZz9seKR8fya6NMvoWi8Tns06jrxzeyzjvU33VWago6ZmiMf7cWkdf_hT9O5d8b6UIeC46vfom9lHwEObb2iI55T71J5c&amp;c=BQa7v_ihdbetQOubnidRuCxNBdY5cOYTZ-bKQPFWeEm78-8UCQbUZg==&amp;ch=ApL6b9g-7RJ41hLsF2jiTI6_uerR0NpJcT16c8eaiIyrSi1JNj6MBA==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Click here to get the full recipe from Whole Foods Market.</em></a>', 'Recipe of the Month- Baked Sweet Potato Fries', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-baked-sweet-potato-fries', '', '', '2014-10-09 16:11:04', '2014-10-09 16:11:04', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2104', '0', 'post', '', '0');
