\r\n	<li><strong>Exercise- </strong>Combine family time with fitness or take your workout indoors. Aim for 30 minutes daily.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Plan- </strong>Never go to a party hungry! Focus your energy on the company and conversation to avoid mindless eating.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Substitute- </strong>Find healthy alternatives to recipes like Greek yogurt in place of sour cream and applesauce in place of butter.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Portion- </strong>Eat and drink from small dishes. Your servings will appear bigger.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Limit- </strong>Allow yourself only one trip through the line. Eat slowly as the first three bites of food are always the best.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor more lower-calorie alternatives and healthy substitutions, <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001Rdgex7ALekzV1tAuYiL5WobXkgB0JyvUbxz4FJYqM1yRWvO2STOOLwIyKYXOE9OTXRzr5XFU5WoakCrfGg3d1q_rzC0k4W-kBHaynDcX5KOs0or_7SLfUdmQl85UCa2QyO0xUD_BP2QiPo5Cw_n9qFu9Nq7A0g8ZHYeZCENZ-mdXemKZ7mf6nVAzYkapSJiype8HFpkOgGjvDTbUiFVzc3gKtLO8IW9jVhsi3-NsrvrIQS4rGmfvLftMhbuK8z0JHguokzJfOUDpQKGBeqj2YHefeEBjxwLEq2lrt2KrDy4=&amp;c=k8qCW_O0LK017Lmbd1uBMgQ2Vrc8WraC_caY8_ohMRaoxyVrC0p3-Q==&amp;ch=TC-NnHouBrnyjjHrw13P2LRARXkFBdedGyDvRkOP2oF4TYz2-Gv8Ng==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>click here</em></a>.', 'Sizing Up Holiday Portions', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sizing-up-holiday-portions', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:20:27', '2014-11-19 21:20:27', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2119', '0', 'post', '', '0');
