ther issues including low back pain, hip or knee pain, and discomfort. Sometimes knee pain is the only sign of a hip problem.\r\n\r\nAlthough the cartilage of the hip joint prevents friction and cushions movement, age and overuse can wear down this protective layer. Hip-strengthening and stretching <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001Rdgex7ALekzV1tAuYiL5WobXkgB0JyvUbxz4FJYqM1yRWvO2STOOLwIyKYXOE9OTz7vj5pCyxJ7uMYWIE8gqPRSparaHyAdgJt-eHvF5qHARsSFs8Q33D618sRGGm6yUeDbf32ZaaTwqquQ7gWsInuRTN78UzCn5pLaDeg0DgjxHOEJhemx4EaBm7lxcEvuMWrfrcQQUTes=&amp;c=k8qCW_O0LK017Lmbd1uBMgQ2Vrc8WraC_caY8_ohMRaoxyVrC0p3-Q==&amp;ch=TC-NnHouBrnyjjHrw13P2LRARXkFBdedGyDvRkOP2oF4TYz2-Gv8Ng==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">exercises</a> can improve range of motion and stability decreasing the risk of injury. Start slowly and work up to multiple sets of each exercise. Seek medical attention if a fall or injury triggered the hip pain, if the pain is intense, or if you can\'t move your leg or hip. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001Rdgex7ALekzV1tAuYiL5WobXkgB0JyvUbxz4FJYqM1yRWvO2STOOLwIyKYXOE9OTijev0qCWasQFzWt8PTjpAposZW5ogLMczesXef6Jtg-_hI8fseU9G22d_eUtXP0-iuzKYSqoAoElyNrsIrpWnpGQxYFnXYnbPLg8gJJTo30W5hwR3f5gegFloKD1DAepRveYGqysLdmC9pwdD_wYALKnHRm8ADQf2Dbi4cms8z2KMYsy6XGrOA==&amp;c=k8qCW_O0LK017Lmbd1uBMgQ2Vrc8WraC_caY8_ohMRaoxyVrC0p3-Q==&amp;ch=TC-NnHouBrnyjjHrw13P2LRARXkFBdedGyDvRkOP2oF4TYz2-Gv8Ng==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', '', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2122-revision-2', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:22:56', '2014-11-19 21:22:56', '', '2122', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2122-revision-2/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2125', '14', '2014-11-10 21:23:13', '2014-11-10 21:23:13', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:390.55pt;margin-top:712.5pt;width:129.75pt;height:55.5pt;\r\n z-index:251658240;mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/1123.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/1123.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1123\" width=\"173\" height=\"74\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->Nuts are a healthy and easy way to get heart-healthy fats, protein, and essential vitamins and minerals. A daily handful of nuts, or about 1.5 ounces, is all you need to reap the nutritional benefits.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Almonds </strong>have the most fiber and calcium of any nut and help control blood sugar and insulin levels.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Walnuts </strong>contain the most omega 3s and alpha linoleic acid for reducing inflammation and preventing heart disease.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cashews </strong>are rich in iron, zinc, and magnesium which help muscle and nerve function.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pistachios </strong>are the most diet-friendly nut with less than 4 calories each. Shelling them slows snacking.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pecans </strong>and <strong>macadamia nuts</strong> have the most calories and least protein per ounce of all nuts.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Peanuts</strong> are actually legumes, not nuts, since they grow underground instead of on trees. Peanuts are high in folate and vitamin E that may help brain health and protect against memory loss.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSeveral studies have shown that including a small amount of nuts can help dieters lose weight. Raw or dry roasted nuts are the best option.  Avoid heavily salted nuts or nuts roasted in oil, as this process can destroy their nutrients. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001Rdgex7ALekzV1tAuYiL5WobXkgB0JyvUbxz4FJYqM1yRWvO2STOOLwIyKYXOE9OTxXZJsBEmgpyYcNYE734Il4YpLMGglH4sC4tm5Vpeg2iVHhcWPTwAsFbDA2Xx6hOvEnWyIcxUNGyRP9Jjsa7eq80vqQPEZZZ00nocmVqCU0G9Q_ydVVVF2m7CIvDSXUCesuWutl59kqn4AjP6zsZUgg==&amp;c=k8qCW_O0LK017Lmbd1uBMgQ2Vrc8WraC_caY8_ohMRaoxyVrC0p3-Q==&amp;ch=TC-NnHouBrnyjjHrw13P2LRARXkFBdedGyDvRkOP2oF4TYz2-Gv8Ng==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Don\'t Go Crazy, But Do Go Nuts!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dont-go-crazy-but-do-go-nuts', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:24:17', '2014-11-19 21:24:17', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2125', '0', 'post', '', '0');
