ender, and daily caloric intake. The quality and source of protein is important, and protein from processed meats should be limited.\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Animal protein from </strong>fish, eggs, and poultry are complete sources of protein and contain all the amino acids our bodies need to function properly.</li>\n	<li><strong>Plant based protein </strong>from beans, nuts, and whole grains contain fiber and can lower the risk of heart disease and certain cancers.</li>\n	<li><strong>Isolated protein powders </strong>like whey, soy, brown rice, and casein are found in powder form and used as supplemental nutrition in addition to a diet already containing high quality protein.</li>\n</ul>\nProtein can aid in weight loss by helping you feel fuller longer and also help build muscle. Too much protein, however, may cause kidney and liver problems. Unlike fats and carbohydrates, protein is not stored in the body and must be replenished. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001pYPOp9M7RW2Q2X14WGJEKb-S7KaaQlmJsZH1TY43F0MWb2L6nmpV6wTb8CdUtMswwfadJoVBJZcONBdu9RQV19plT_b-OpKrx_d6s6m3OLt1D29F86JdWcEp-MCpG2AvrhJjMjbH3U5vx9J9eFcAIEFRV_088KXR1VFwqcPlNlI0WFw_emxeh_J2OcWSjV5hGccHhEI1VgtYGx4uf7aivw==&amp;c=F0iBj5wku9Rh1OVlgsK-srf9yu2cvUjYKjL9M4pZcQRj7-hpjOwwRA==&amp;ch=LtdIU694q0tfaLU5kzBvBEW-wk1VRnSMcVSwDWEPtNGQss4VF3tqSg==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The Power of Protein', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2142-revision', '', '', '2014-12-16 22:38:59', '2014-12-16 22:38:59', '', '2142', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2142-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
