ise consistently and spend time outside daily.</li>\n	<li>Limit caffeine and nicotine in the afternoon and evening hours.</li>\n	<li>Avoid large meals and spicy food before bedtime.</li>\n	<li>Keep a notepad by your bed to jot down lingering thoughts and tasks.</li>\n	<li>Avoid backlit screens close to bedtime.</li>\n	<li>Wind down with a relaxing evening routine.</li>\n</ul>\nSleep deprivation can lead to a greater appetite and weight gain, increased risk of diabetes, and lower immunity. To make sure you are getting adequate sleep, keep your bedroom cool, around 65°. Your bedroom should also be free from any noise and light. Consider using blackout curtains, eye shades, ear plugs, noise machines, humidifiers, or fans. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaWfXAem6hIoFoV03AlmVEszdh7o_sx4EMVOu3ScVaX0KBmQsnODGc1bmGgJXLdcQdT1pX0Tec17ZTjCn095v4B1F_XfMugdg4svKLxUOZN7lBLMr8OXA0l9Nd-mNKsA0Wtclaeno9sQN6WNxjD97JAg=&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'A Good Night\'s Sleep', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2160-revision', '', '', '2015-01-21 20:30:08', '2015-01-21 20:30:08', '', '2160', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2160-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2162', '14', '2015-01-13 20:30:28', '2015-01-13 20:30:28', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:0;margin-top:-15pt;width:104.25pt;height:111pt;z-index:251658240;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:left;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/463.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"http://ih.constantcontact.com/fs196/1103500019310/img/463.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.463\" width=\"139\" height=\"148\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->\r\n\r\n<em>When you lose weight, where does the fat go?</em>\r\n\r\nHave you ever wondered what happens to fat when you lose weight? In short, it\'s exhaled into thin air. That\'s right, about 84% of fat burned is converted into carbon dioxide and breathed out through the lungs. The remaining 16% becomes water that is excreted out of the body through sweat and bodily functions.\r\n\r\nTo lose fat, science still proves you must burn more calories than you are consuming. One pound of fat is equivalent to 3,500 calories, so in order to lose one pound, you must create a 3,500 calorie deficit through eating less or exercising more. Cutting 500 calories from the diet each day adds up to a 3,500 calorie deficit in one week. It\'s much easier to consume calories than it is to burn them, so balancing weight loss efforts with both diet and exercise will produce better results. Resistance exercises like weight lifting and strength training can increase the metabolism to burn more calories even at rest, so aim to include strengthening exercise 2-3 times a week. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra5jMvXl4T1TU3ieubvo4zGyvGBFTbX1lyw0ozqRotVUC_dtvswctB05Efd5t3r3CQL1UMCqQGCYH5swoCWNQsT6JiSb9D1kpsVt0IxYEgJCZ6N_-LpR5TSjuzP_Iry-2bcui_9iaCzJ1nw2hK8yVBM-2uXhAAr5lPdf3nbnGqOFgE=&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The Disappearing Act of Fat', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-disappearing-act-of-fat', '', '', '2015-01-21 20:31:11', '2015-01-21 20:31:11', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2162', '0', 'post', '', '0');
