p patterns in kids. Adults who spend at least 4 hours of leisure time in front of a TV are twice as likely to have a heart attack. Screen time for children is especially habit-forming. Studies show the more time children are in front of screens, the harder time they have turning them off as they become older. Children consume on average almost 170 additional calories per day for every hour they watch TV.\r\n\r\nWith obesity on the rise in children and adults, take active steps to limit screen time in your family. Turn off mobile phones and televisions during meal time and eat only in the kitchen. Do <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra5LmxGIz2R4Bzb_seTcualn8H75JkI8DumvviOo7R45tUJAgVxw_NRd_yL3Dv7PMaO_RW0Kw7Gmia9Heh_rfUO9EZSS2Lr4L3rUqyghle5PQuf1CJUqHltB8nDnAaLOQtP_DLIVAq-cspNCr0ajapgj2KtcUIFBuCX8cp8tVGIYiS__4cwvqZ2Ukg-uPvlx0FKytfZEM4sqq8=&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">something active</a> or play a game after meal time. Keep track of your screen time by using this <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra5NCTumQoac2YGGvdZUAQPeDz0ztzZ2YXc0Y7YWIntx7RZk62QMCXw73PUMRYvEgDQHBYRU_MvKVaNg7F2UtHnv4w6CXf5U1A826893dkg9EQSnNRIYzQTsc5Sp_-J22NyCw38DUyRp9zDw9Y1YaK2Snawz6MBrWVInhhXk76QAc4DEEizBq74hQ==&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">activity log</a>. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra53zqVRuoLgcOysDNzbD4qI_LeD-cz8I2ugL_zqu1_44jNAZJLUL52-ov9ykYulg8VZfGlAi6xdCINOlvD4Oya4URBg6lKRQ55z76sL5WHkvxOXxh-828ByZzEmFxHL7wzpmmrcYimg6ylctZ-3BnjUnpYnBvxLf4Uo-IPiPVnzww=&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAx