 is also more vulnerable to injury. Additionally, age and overuse from manual labor and sports can cause a breakdown of soft tissues in the shoulder region.\r\n\r\nThe small rotator cuff muscles that surround the shoulder joint must be kept strong to maintain maximum stability and function. Weakness in these muscles can lead to a host of injuries. Shoulder strengthening exercises can be done at home or at the gym and include the <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra5yUyId-eEP83p4pHSLLRmDo7dSCeaypNWJiK-71u1qUPU02Q3zrWUUsAXIavz8HK8a3uTE7aFsjzld_BoXQLi2ibftwdrC2xUeG80KJX2ENHOfRUAPA3CBI2J7iUDLsD0vtCXfTXn311J6uZ3dr9egYyoQaG43u5g&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">shoulder press</a>, push ups, <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra5nkfSlnFTECFkiZcnv3s3t9930uTfFqyveHlQXvO5ql3DCKmPYTAtUlz_jIcpGhZWZaIOKqdS5ppuFinD6vGLLFydl7t0wy4ox0MOck3X5XyXuuQwfGzu8Ky1Y06Ridgx-GP8XryWksHAijC3x0qBSXsXJ2TjxC_U&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">lateral raises</a>, and rows. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001QEdfrCk38wc9wGKG4KqGASpzDdjqzdVDpUpcCL7yY2NN2EtlkgGqaa_B0jGbsra5YcYRfGvNyBCwm4Z_DMDULifX8u3yjHM8OMFB-SLvKSMDnAFusuUZ2ASmSH8tdzruDyEx8Q93neP7QMruxZQxRTv4l3JwiCgVEbnotm20xHDfRe0VVEmUzc2zdAbposDKedkEvrVwFw2iu5f5IoiQaA==&amp;c=nSXqgoINyKvY866MZQoeTgKSb7tIhZcdXixL2kfeBGIs5wAjbJHkqA==&amp;ch=EgjAxqWueYi4QKp9JlhsQ2kjwOzV0kziAu1YL_xIJq8VA4Ihr3brFQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Resistance band exercises</a> can help target front and rear rotator cuff muscles. It\'s important to include stretching into your shoulder workout to maintain flexibility and range of motion. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=