INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2184', '14', '2015-02-06 20:28:27', '2015-02-06 20:28:27', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"\" style=\'position:absolute;\r\n margin-left:-329.45pt;margin-top:-15pt;width:135.75pt;height:89.25pt;\r\n z-index:251658240;mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;\r\n mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:line\' o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"https://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/6b127529-6776-4aeb-a030-1d791b0f5fcb.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"https://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/6b127529-6776-4aeb-a030-1d791b0f5fcb.jpg\" alt=\"\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1256\" width=\"181\" height=\"119\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->The heart has a big job for such a small organ. Measuring only the size of your fist, your heart shuttles 2,000 gallons of oxygen-rich blood through about 60,000 miles of blood vessles, or more than two trips around the equator, each day. As the body\'s lifeline, take care of your heart so it takes care of you:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Eat well</strong> by including healthy fats found in fish, walnuts, avocados, flaxseed and olive oil.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Stress less</strong> to reduce the risk of cortisol causing cholesterol deposits to rupture. These deposits could travel to the heart or brain, leading to a heart attack or stroke.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Exercise daily</strong> by aiming for at least 30 minutes of moderate-intensity activity most days of the week.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA family history of cardiovascular disease, smoking, being overweight, and having hypertension or diabetes can all increase your risk for heart disease. Give your heart some special attention by taking precautions against the disease before it\'s too late. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0017mQ0Vc9mTDayFEc5IUUHkUY6YeDaODTbYps_BuCFoJMOHhp6JwtqYnfH-_A9nNXL302vDHdwb7epidqjgNPHLksuFhHJEGlNV4WrlBmdE3l8hGleeTM-D2sLZgEkFblUDOfR_OUp_-oObFxKkABXJtZFJcpx-93YqKwjyxQbg7_i9Y1RAQ2QOBFbkaXIwlnO6U5fTAbVo58aH-O650BNT6B5-dyEZjqu3iufufR3Z0imDwWdvLHXR10nu3BZH623&amp;c=7kuIi6nbcTS4KiiKEBSTgbdPa3ftbimuf4k16i1FNU9V3ULGVwbfYQ==&amp;ch=ozkcvucfpT9MG5m3KdXxOTGo7_ZcgY8FarDYLgtYwrTS_vtQouxHVQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The Heart of it All', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-heart-of-it-all', '', '', '2015-02-26 20:29:38', '2015-02-26 20:29:38', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2184', '0', 'post', '', '0');
