INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2186', '14', '2015-02-12 20:29:51', '2015-02-12 20:29:51', '<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\"\r\n coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\"\r\n filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\r\n </v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1027\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"Food sources of vitamin D\"\r\n style=\'position:absolute;margin-left:0;margin-top:-15pt;width:104.25pt;\r\n height:104.25pt;z-index:251658240;mso-wrap-distance-left:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:3.75pt;mso-wrap-distance-right:3.75pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-bottom:3.75pt;mso-position-horizontal:left;\r\n mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical-relative:line\'\r\n o:allowoverlap=\"f\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"https://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/2442fa52-6892-45da-b8f4-238f50107771.jpg\"/>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img src=\"https://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/2442fa52-6892-45da-b8f4-238f50107771.jpg\" alt=\"Food sources of vitamin D\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1260\" width=\"139\" height=\"139\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /><!--[endif]-->It\'s estimated that 40-75% of Americans are deficient in vitamin D. Although the sunshine vitamin can be synthesized in the skin from sun exposure, it\'s only naturally occurring in seafood, egg yolks, and mushrooms. Other foods like milk, orange juice, and cereal are fortified with the nutrient. Vitamin D is an immune enhancer and can also protect against the common cold and flu. Research also shows the vitamin can play a role in reducing asthma symptoms as well as preventing colon, breast, and prostate cancer.\r\n\r\nThe NIH recommends 600IU of vitamin D for all adults age 18-70. Most people meet some vitamin D needs through sun exposure, however living in higher latitudes, air pollution, darker skin tones, sunscreen, and age can all decrease the amount absorbed. Additionally, gut health can affect absorption through food and supplements, especially in people who have digestive issues like celiac disease and Chron\'s. To determine if you are getting enough vitamin D, talk to your doctor about a simple blood test or order your Vitamin D, 25-Hydroxy test through <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0017mQ0Vc9mTDayFEc5IUUHkUY6YeDaODTbYps_BuCFoJMOHhp6JwtqYravzpza4PkSOYjitk0eN9XPmNdzsvh33I16atsRWbwU5KXpWKPw2ugMKXz-CrNhUMRwODmfofjwYmpXQVzoAUel3qwIp0UqHulWWU_zXttiu2TwYYDzEWAqzrW2jAHIj085jEXLomN-obH1nXhl7EmaScwpalxZTkG0apzNtHES&amp;c=7kuIi6nbcTS4KiiKEBSTgbdPa3ftbimuf4k16i1FNU9V3ULGVwbfYQ==&amp;ch=ozkcvucfpT9MG5m3KdXxOTGo7_ZcgY8FarDYLgtYwrTS_vtQouxHVQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling\'s network of labs</a>. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0017mQ0Vc9mTDayFEc5IUUHkUY6YeDaODTbYps_BuCFoJMOHhp6JwtqYsjZ9TDHJclAy41ha56HVRkDL_77aCS9I26dSIDPk41l7Nlf5JKhL7l4KWYzBgWhCNoOoSU6cMlOZ0NWDBlKAv5HJ-VEaOBtPH2XyaVv0Y1p-_9xHXLgkwnh97VRl70q_jKC9La2-O1o2iDoT39VkiMEBwqt8HbxqHpxn5nmMzND&amp;c=7kuIi6nbcTS4KiiKEBSTgbdPa3ftbimuf4k16i1FNU9V3ULGVwbfYQ==&amp;ch=ozkcvucfpT9MG5m3KdXxOTGo7_ZcgY8FarDYLgtYwrTS_vtQouxHVQ==\" shape=\"rect\" target=\"_blank\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The D Deficiency', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-d-deficiency', '', '', '2015-02-26 20:30:24', '2015-02-26 20:30:24', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.c