INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2247', '14', '2015-04-20 11:13:34', '2015-04-20 17:13:34', '<div>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/fbde8dfc-10fc-4815-a5f7-7b25712882db.jpg?a=1120545671013\" alt=\"\" width=\"115\" height=\"172\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1326\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Low back pain is the single leading cause of disability world wide. As much as 80% of the population will experience a back problem at some point in their life. Small adjustments in your body mechanics and lifestyle habits can make a significant impact on the prevention or treatment of back pain.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strengthen core, back and abdominal muscles.</li>\r\n	<li>Use proper posture when standing and sitting. Keeps ears over the shoulders and engage the core to prevent slouching.</li>\r\n	<li>Sit less and move more.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain a healthy weight.</li>\r\n	<li>Lift properly, bending at the knees.</li>\r\n	<li>Adjust computer monitors and reading material to eye level.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Frequent use of a stability ball has been shown to decrease discomfort to those who suffer from back pain. Ab balls can strengthen the entire core, not just isolated muscle groups. Try replacing your desk chair with an ab ball for portions of your day or using one in conjunction with regular workout sessions. <a href=\"http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/backpain.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\">More</a></div>\r\n</div>', 'Preventing Low Back Pain', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'preventing-low-back-pain', '', '', '2015-04-23 11:14:02', '2015-04-23 17:14:02', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2247', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2248', '14', '2015-04-23 11:14:02', '2015-04-23 17:14:02', '<div>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/fbde8dfc-10fc-4815-a5f7-7b25712882db.jpg?a=1120545671013\" alt=\"\" width=\"115\" height=\"172\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1326\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Low back pain is the single leading cause of disability world wide. As much as 80% of the population will experience a back problem at some point in their life. Small adjustments in your body mechanics and lifestyle habits can make a significant impact on the prevention or treatment of back pain.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strengthen core, back and abdominal muscles.</li>\r\n	<li>Use proper posture when standing and sitting. Keeps ears over the shoulders and engage the core to prevent slouching.</li>\r\n	<li>Sit less and move more.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain a healthy weight.</li>\r\n	<li>Lift properly, bending at the knees.</li>\r\n	<li>Adjust computer monitors and reading material to eye level.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Frequent use of a stability ball has been shown to decrease discomfort to those who suffer from back pain. Ab balls can strengthen the entire core, not just isolated muscle groups. Try replacing your desk chair with an ab ball for portions of your day or using one in conjunction with regular workout sessions. <a href=\"http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/backpain.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\">More</a></div>\r\n</div>', 'Preventing Low Back Pain', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2247-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-23 11:14:02', '2015-04-23 17:14:02', '', '2247', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2247-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2249', '14', '2015-04-24 11:14:15', '2015-04-24 17:14:15', '<p align=\"left\"><a class=\"imgCaptionAnchor\" href=\"http://www.myrecipes.com/recipe/blueberry-orange-parfaits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\"><img src=\"http://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/8a9dcaab-ecb4-4a5c-b4d3-f1ba6e0cd0da.jpg?a=1120545671013\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"204\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1324\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /></a>Prepare these layered parfaits in a seal-tight container for lunch or an on-the-go snack. To make life even easier, purchase already peeled orange sections in the refrigerated part of the produce section.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Combine turbinado sugar (optional) with grated orange rind and plain Greek yogurt.</li>\r\n	<li>Repeat layers of blueberries, yogurt mixture, and oranges.</li>\r\n	<li>Sprinkle wheat germ over each serving and chill or serve immediately.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>Mix and match your favorite combinations of berries and fruits for a healthy and quick snack. The protein in Greek yogurt and fiber in the fruit will keep you filling full and satisfied!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div> <a href=\"http://www.myrecipes.com/recipe/blueberry-orange-parfaits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\">Click here to get the full recipe from Myrecipes.com.</a></div>', 'Recipe of the Month- Blueberry Orange Parfaits', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-blueberry-orange-parfaits', '', '', '2015-04-23 11:14:54', '2015-04-23 17:14:54', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2249', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2250', '14', '2015-04-23 11:14:54', '2015-04-23 17:14:54', '<p align=\"left\"><a class=\"imgCaptionAnchor\" href=\"http://www.myrecipes.com/recipe/blueberry-orange-parfaits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\"><img src=\"http://files.ctctcdn.com/e660abde001/8a9dcaab-ecb4-4a5c-b4d3-f1ba6e0cd0da.jpg?a=1120545671013\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"204\" name=\"ACCOUNT.IMAGE.1324\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"5\" vspace=\"5\" /></a>Prepare these layered parfaits in a seal-tight container for lunch or an on-the-go snack. To make life even easier, purchase already peeled orange sections in the refrigerated part of the produce section.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Combine turbinado sugar (optional) with grated orange rind and plain Greek yogurt.</li>\r\n	<li>Repeat layers of blueberries, yogurt mixture, and oranges.</li>\r\n	<li>Sprinkle wheat germ over each serving and chill or serve immediately.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>Mix and match your favorite combinations of berries and fruits for a healthy and quick snack. The protein in Greek yogurt and fiber in the fruit will keep you filling full and satisfied!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div> <a href=\"http://www.myrecipes.com/recipe/blueberry-orange-parfaits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" shape=\"rect\">Click here to get the full recipe from Myrecipes.com.</a></div>', 'Recipe of the Month- Blueberry Orange Parfaits', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2249-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-23 11:14:54', '2015-04-23 17:14:54', '', '2249', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/2249-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2252', '14', '2015-01-16 14:58:15', '2015-01-16 14:58:15', 'Sterling Wellness Solutions is looking for the best and brightest individuals to join a dynamic and talented team. Our multi-dimensional approach to wellness requires creative thinking, industry knowledge, and a unified mission of introducing wellness in an exciting new light. Please use the form below to contact us if you are interested in employment with our team.\r\n<h4><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Current positions available</strong></span>:</h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Registered Nurse (New Orleans Area)</strong>\r\n\r\nSeeking an ambitious Primary Care Nurse to serve the greater New Orleans area. Must be a degreed and licensed professional with 3-5 years of experience as a Registered Nurse or Nurse Practitioner. Early mornings and significant local travel required. Requires motivational health coaching, clinical biometric knowledge, and computer proficiency. Responsible for engaging and positively impacting individuals and groups through preventive wellness programs including diabetes, weight management, and smoking cessation. Requires scheduling and facilitating wellness screenings, providing intensive onsite and telephonic health coaching, and overseeing wellness incentive program. Serious and qualified inquires only.\r\n\r\n<strong>Program Manager </strong>\r\n\r\nSeeking an enthusiastic and motivated Program Manager.  Must be a degreed professional with 3-5 years of experience in customer services, business to business service, and/or program management.  Requires excellent written and communication skills, public speaking skills, ability to communicate wellness industry-related information during and after account implementation, corporate business experience, and proficiency in Excel, Word, PowerPoint, and Publisher.  Group insurance or Human Resource experience a plus.  Must be able to work independently and in team settings under high pressure with deadlines.  This position will act as the primary liaison to key accounts and develop long-term relationships with clients. Serious and qualified inquires only.\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[gravityform id=\"1\" name=\"Careers\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"]', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-16 14:58:15', '2015-01-16 14:58:15', '', '8', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/8-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
