INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2273', '14', '2015-05-28 14:32:27', '2015-05-28 20:32:27', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Avocado-Bowl.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2260\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Avocado-Bowl-150x150.png\" alt=\"Avocado Bowl\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Combining avocados with eggs packs a double dose of healthy omega-3 fats and protein. Avocados contain more potassium than bananas, making this a nutrition-rich way to start the day.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Split 1 avocado and remove the pit.</li>\r\n	<li>Make the hole a bit bigger by scooping out some of the fruit with a spoon.</li>\r\n	<li>Crack one egg into each half, season to taste, and bake at 350° for 15 minutes, or until the egg is cooked to your liking.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTry different versions of your egg bowl by seasoning it with red pepper flakes, onions, peppers, low-fat cheese, or herbs. This recipe makes two servings, but can be doubled easily for a quick meatless weekday dinner.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001Yho2juwkbO5_KdeGEDh3R4ERjwVQ-GgjaywEnxDVJAx09d_bwzX00YcbExHmHJDP6b4sH_i4i7zmYwHU18Q2fX_Usl2I6n_6S5_DiHTd2yrxkjhNc-ZxVLU4zhBWKNX8PxgSgXiDd0FWw9cashjeQ8KSFbfLWIPVQbxOMp1NXOblelTbwcCDK0-_64YTf7qD3sFzhKcNwkgP7h3rCO4plat2l1VZxGXa&amp;c=lOF5qHyC3fxbBM-TaXUETFJmGSnmIn7f07KKzJMuCS3tDUXBUwvLsA==&amp;ch=_3yMhgxP2yb0LuyxoHtUL_A2-XaKoaqAT2nL_3KMZM4nrBVF4x0pWQ==\"><em>Click here to get the full recipe from Greatist.com.</em></a>', 'Recipe of the Month- Avocado Egg Bowl', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-avocado-egg-bowl', '', '', '2015-05-21 14:33:15', '2015-05-21 20:33:15', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2273', '0', 'post', '', '0');
