INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2300', '14', '2015-06-30 11:28:52', '2015-06-30 17:28:52', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/parfaits.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2289\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/parfaits-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"parfaits\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Make a boom at your Independence Day picnic with a patriotic parfait.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In a large bowl, stir low-fat or Greek yogurt with almond extract or vanilla.</li>\r\n	<li>Fold in light whipped topping (optional)</li>\r\n	<li>Alternate layers of blueberries, raspberries, or strawberries with yogurt mixture.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTry different versions of your parfait by including a section of star fruit at the top, bananas, or strawberry or blueberry flavored yogurt. For some extra protein and healthy fats, sprinkle the top with granola, flax, or chia seeds.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=001GMAWedr49fh3ISFKxGgKn_hpr1BKvGPvuOYgGnFK3O6Wc8YBcVoUHkEFa3OCvx--YH8p8BtboIFAyYalFoUdu8HMG3dvVw15CEzk4cZwxISeTS8_jze-PDv7UlS32ZiBPuvRTBaBWgSPIjdG89El1aiVOLXlj4ho0eqe-555Ivg=\"><em>Click here to get the full recipe from Better Homes &amp; Gardens.</em></a>', 'Recipe of the Month- Red, White, and Blue Parfaits', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-red-white-and-blue-parfaits', '', '', '2015-06-18 11:29:44', '2015-06-18 17:29:44', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2300', '0', 'post', '', '0');
