INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2310', '14', '2015-07-06 14:08:13', '2015-07-06 20:08:13', '<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\',sans-serif; color: #d78519;\">Sitting is the New Smoking</span></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"></p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/sitting-smoking.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2311\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/sitting-smoking-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"sitting smoking\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>From the car to the desk to the couch to the bed, the average American is sedentary for almost 21 hours a day. Medical experts have compared the risks of excessive sitting to the same dangerous effects of smoking including heart disease, diabetes, cancer, and depression.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>\"Five hours or more of sedentary sitting is the health equivalent to smoking 1.25 packs of cigarettes.\"</em></strong><em> </em>-Dr. David Agus\r\n\r\nNew research shows the benefits of 30-60 minutes of exercise may not be enough to counteract prolonged sitting. Too much sitting can be linked to:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Slower metabolism</li>\r\n	<li>20% decrease in good cholesterol after sitting for 2 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Poor circulation and blood flow</li>\r\n	<li>Less effective insulin use which leads to diabetes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">Take a stand against sitting by moving every hour, taking frequent stretch breaks, standing while on the phone, and holding walking meetings. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001BLfvQ7vk2lv5d-8pDscYAs9o9UfbpjwpqVWFzoyV5YXDBdhpQ1MpqOi2DmxrPfpakfh17L5RVmcd6Fm7MACOpAYlNXWY799WNNMLh18-7MKk2zoHODSj_TgE0w-_FGD3eub6HQfl2_1QJZhd7veEK44oI0naGcKbDptTw-mbaxOzKDK0r2bmW1JK0rCPGFPMuSG34BjK2H4uBN00vhVGueAEMYZKn5ZT&amp;c=A6VqcGzdILDIHgDbP2a_XZsRgpgAXS4o3O07u-v7bGlcT7zo_075dg==&amp;ch=GKqa7GS_i1S77Vdt7rhpPdd8UejTI1yLyGNYCUguPe8-w91Nr5PTlA==\"><em>More</em></a></p>', 'Beware of the Chair', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'beware-of-the-chair', '', '', '2015-07-16 14:09:34', '2015-07-16 20:09:34', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2310', '0', 'post', '', '0');
