INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2318', '14', '2015-07-17 14:12:19', '2015-07-17 20:12:19', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/glutenfree-850x638.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2319\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/glutenfree-850x638-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"glutenfree-850x638\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Much attention is being drawn to gluten as increasingly more people are diagnosed with Celiac Disease, gluten sensitivity or intolerance, and wheat allergies. Those with gluten sensitivity often experience serious gastrointestinal changes, inflammation, or bloating.\r\n\r\nGluten is a protein found in many grains and acts as a glue to bind ingredients together. The acronym BROWS can help you identify foods with gluten; barley, rye, oats, wheat, and spelt. Gluten is not naturally occurring in oats, however they are often harvested and processed along with wheat, contaminating them with gluten proteins. Although these grain products have been in the food supply for hundreds of years, modern food processing has hybridized these grains to create a product with higher gluten content. This process could explain the sharp increase in gluten sensitivity in recent years.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Do not attempt to self-diagnose without seeking the expert opinion of a physician. These grains are an essential source of fiber, minerals, and B vitamins, and shouldn\'t be avoided unless advised by a medical professional. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001BLfvQ7vk2lv5d-8pDscYAs9o9UfbpjwpqVWFzoyV5YXDBdhpQ1MpqNlrTO8NqfF0Xly-rhfmRySo0tB2fVJQTrxWPt_9HXQMrY0SKzKwEKaIot0PC-HYpUkBPBM1UAOX8LWy5PhgM_FJk42bEVydfCZFKTyHSdSw_YsjROe0V_s=&amp;c=A6VqcGzdILDIHgDbP2a_XZsRgpgAXS4o3O07u-v7bGlcT7zo_075dg==&amp;ch=GKqa7GS_i1S77Vdt7rhpPdd8UejTI1yLyGNYCUguPe8-w91Nr5PTlA==\"><em>More</em></a></p>', 'Is Gluten-Free Right for Me?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'is-gluten-free-right-for-me-2', '', '', '2015-07-16 14:13:17', '2015-07-16 20:13:17', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2318', '0', 'post', '', '0');
