INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2322', '14', '2015-07-21 14:13:38', '2015-07-21 20:13:38', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/walking.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2324\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/walking-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"walking\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>No, we\'re not talking about the clothes you wear! But now that we have your attention, walking shorts is a new term used to describe brief walks lasting as little as 10 minutes. Many people struggle to carve out time for a 30-60 minute workout. Walking briskly in 10 minute increments can improve blood pressure, bone density, mental focus, and lung capacity. Each time you walk, your body\'s metabolism burns more calories to help with weight control as well.\r\n\r\nFor anyone looking to begin an exercise routine, a 10 minute walk is a great place to start. Slowly build up to repeating this 10-minute walking routine three times a day for a total of 30 minutes. Grab a buddy to ramp up the frequency, intensity, and time of your walks. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001BLfvQ7vk2lv5d-8pDscYAs9o9UfbpjwpqVWFzoyV5YXDBdhpQ1MpqCscfgD0RKhQgHnE0TOHOmyZeSAOa6HHZOYbIZd1rwJik0Swn2IpawRV49mIZ8gH2iktpSQJfM7B756gGQp8biPV7KEDn-FErjR9Vvh5wKNkl5xsiTHGj4krxNr3GsU0ce5ALNlkMCJ18uaume7wcq4L03UH5kTfxWyGZcdTglfLv3_4mbfMLH1YoxGyBxOOZg==&amp;c=A6VqcGzdILDIHgDbP2a_XZsRgpgAXS4o3O07u-v7bGlcT7zo_075dg==&amp;ch=GKqa7GS_i1S77Vdt7rhpPdd8UejTI1yLyGNYCUguPe8-w91Nr5PTlA==\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Benefits of Walking Shorts', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'benefits-of-walking-shorts', '', '', '2015-07-16 14:14:58', '2015-07-16 20:14:58', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2322', '0', 'post', '', '0');
