INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2326', '14', '2015-07-30 14:15:25', '2015-07-30 20:15:25', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Fire-and-Ice.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2323\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Fire-and-Ice-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Fire and Ice\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>From the contrasting flavors and colors of the fresh vegetables and spices, Fire and Ice salad is a refreshing combination of peak-season produce. Cool down on a hot summer day with this chilled salad.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Slice tomatoes, bell peppers, and onion.</li>\r\n	<li>Combine vinegar, spices, sugar, and water to prepare dressing.</li>\r\n	<li>Boil dressing for 1 minute and pour hot dressing over vegetables. Chill.</li>\r\n	<li>Before serving, peel and slice cucumber and toss with vegetables.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTry different combinations using various colors of peppers, cherry or heirloom tomatoes, and spices. For a heart-healthy boost, drizzle some olive oil on top.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001BLfvQ7vk2lv5d-8pDscYAs9o9UfbpjwpqVWFzoyV5YXDBdhpQ1MpqNlrTO8NqfF0gqbzElK3aeWZ5-X9DufNJ2hRbjP06H4zTkJiZEkYg0JUR-j_EQtUMq1r71ZcYmYr63p3CUppqlm6C36foTt2nFqIa4D95auo3aXGQITYe3xPVvc1AzdRb8TwZkzmOmV_HvowXmQkP3eFMqGHpVyIfg==&amp;c=A6VqcGzdILDIHgDbP2a_XZsRgpgAXS4o3O07u-v7bGlcT7zo_075dg==&amp;ch=GKqa7GS_i1S77Vdt7rhpPdd8UejTI1yLyGNYCUguPe8-w91Nr5PTlA==\"><em>Click here to get the full recipe from AllRecipes.</em></a>', 'Recipe of the Month - Fire & Ice Salad', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'recipe-of-the-month-fire-and-ice-salad', '', '', '2015-07-16 14:16:09', '2015-07-16 20:16:09', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2326', '0', 'post', '', '0');
