INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2335', '14', '2015-08-03 12:43:37', '2015-08-03 18:43:37', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Positivity.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2336\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Positivity-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Positivity\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The right attitude may be the key to longevity. Smiling, laughter, and complimentary praise all release endorphins and serotonin, feel good chemicals that can decrease stress and anxiety. Humor improves immune cell function that helps ward of illness.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>\"Your mind is a powerful thing. When you fill it with positive thoughts, your life will start to change.\"</em></strong><em> -Julie Voris</em>\r\n\r\nIf you aren\'t naturally positive, experts recommend trying one of the following repeatedly until it becomes second nature:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Shift pessimism to positive self-talk.</li>\r\n	<li>Practice gratitude by recognizing things you are most thankful for and writing them down.</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer or give to those less fortunate.</li>\r\n	<li>Surround yourself with those who bring you joy.</li>\r\n	<li>Laugh. Read or listen to comedic entertainment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA positive outlook leads to better coping strategies during hard times, and is also thought to lead to other healthy behaviors like diet and exercise. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001ifDocx7sEl8O4OqBmlnLntYnann2-SHHYnevnveP4LgEZsN7D8StpZ1zRJ7CWUhxR-MTatEjsB5HqWz4Kr9rl8VGpiGjEzq6ckLDX6EFhxpr7u43qznsuQD7Kt2mobKxbrHiudEfJYnn0JM8ePHRruJJGuDb6He_Nt0se01-2fakvUS8SVbJ7mrg9piWphqE047oWshtd9tjCMPAnf9I6MoJUiPif4mbecerNg9QRHxP5UNm2zZ7OSeLjgRyRgHBE_A5THW_dFBXvGF7tVf8urH0gY9am4-4&amp;c=s4ugFE-FmHqmsE8qZmqyHnF5tXgXR7E8lo45Da6M7-9WRMUjZzXnfQ==&amp;ch=R1d81_NR-gXMVvpUwqOU3AgxAIJO2NLIKON3fMYW5cgxguqp5Trx-w==\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The Power of Positivity', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-power-of-positivity', 