INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2339', '14', '2015-08-10 12:46:08', '2015-08-10 18:46:08', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/healthy-snack.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2340\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/healthy-snack-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"healthy snack\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Healthy snacks between 100-150 calories can prevent the drop in blood sugar between meals keeping your energy levels, blood sugar levels, and mental abilities steady. Since your brain uses glucose as fuel, feed it wisely with healthy combinations of protein and carbohydrates.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1/2 banana + 1 tablespoon of peanut butter</li>\r\n	<li>1/2 cup cottage cheese + 1/2 cup fruit</li>\r\n	<li>1/2 cup Greek yogurt + 1 tablespoon of dried cranberries</li>\r\n	<li>10 baby carrots + 2 tablespoons of hummus</li>\r\n	<li>2 hard boiled eggs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNever go longer than 4 hours without food, and don\'t confuse a snack for a treat. Sip water regularly throughout the day to keep energy levels high, and be mindful that hunger is not confused for thirst. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001ifDocx7sEl8O4OqBmlnLntYnann2-SHHYnevnveP4LgEZsN7D8StpYq1WQJoqchPHlo6m_J4GsZwyRLjX0bM3vHWNerolozPehsWIsJ0xBiHyLPa8jKoEpiN2pq9kU2sOeX_xaBUfbUWo5PbIE9RTzYSWpaAkdhpyPtRAU-edoyezgUPc9s5RG8yGxDQjbw3zgc79NwdZstQV80fgT9vkd5o6y7aiXAKB_Mwg6asfVAWisgUK-XEeQ==&amp;c=s4ugFE-FmHqmsE8qZmqyHnF5tXgXR7E8lo45Da6M7-9WRMUjZzXnfQ==&amp;ch=R1d81_NR-gXMVvpUwqOU3AgxAIJO2NLIKON3fMYW5cgxguqp5Trx-w==\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Healthy Snack Attack', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'healthy-snack-attack', '', '', '2015-08-13 12:48:07', '2015-08-13 18:48:07', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2339', '0', 'post', '', '0');
