INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2362', '14', '2015-09-10 16:00:27', '2015-09-10 22:00:27', 'A healthy breakfast doesn\'t require much effort, but with over 100 varieties of cereal in many grocery stores, the options can seem endless. Narrow down your selection by focusing on the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2359\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/superior-cereal-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"superior cereal\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Whole grains</strong>- should be listed as the first ingredient.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sugar</strong>- is often added in multiple forms under different names like cane syrup or agave nectar. Avoid cereals with sugar in the first 3 ingredients. Dried fruit in cereal can be coated in sugar, so add fresh fruit instead. Look for less than 8 grams per serving.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fiber</strong>- look for at least 3 grams of dietary fiber. Whole grain flours and added fiber like inulin are not good indicators of quality fiber, so look for bran, wheat germ, or steel-cut oat cereals.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Fats- </b>avoid cereals with trans fat or more than 1 gram of saturated fat. Many granolas marketed as healthy choices are packed with unhealthy fat.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nChildren\'s cereals are particularly bad culprits of artificial food dyes and sugar. Some kids\' cereals contain more than 40% sugar, more than a glazed doughnut!  Breakfast can jump-start the metabolism and fuel your brain and body with energy it needs to succeed. Breakfast eaters tend to be thinner than their counterparts and also make healthier decisions throughout the day. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0011tvD9udTy8I7jbxUV6aMlIvh4_sKeAIGLbkomj7XrM3UiQ4bXrSsP5Bz3nkAcYVg9N6WEXDAjsnx0ttRBstAjQMxGxODFsGfyATnTkff_s7CgpNqrV12ZxDpDZbnX2yOegXAbnjOVg_RDTp_9Cppk-NvQ-PmJjFLr8dCUViszJ0ongbvrhVyaCKdy_B3TNbOwppAqN0A_dJ66eKZU_Fuqwz8-TBnykRQ_hsjvD2mdi5pGI6k-yufYaRXsO4zUXwbuysRzVXcKqk=&amp;c=3Neb1x8oCvXYazvdgjkHUftrjbnj96Yq_jxUtKLEbIumwUaXJ5w2iQ==&amp;ch=WXO2tZCDiMqrDGYp-D3oBS5nFNUpNxhxt5DmlMLPRB4DSeoYVR-ITA==\"><em>More</em></a>', 'Superior Cereal', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'superior-cereal', '', '', '2015-09-21 16:02:38', '2015-09-21 22:02:38', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2362', '0', 'post', '', '0');
