INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2372', '14', '2015-09-28 16:04:33', '2015-09-28 22:04:33', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/zucchini-pizza-bites.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2357\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/zucchini-pizza-bites-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"zucchini-pizza-bites\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>These bite-sized finger foods are perfect for a meatless-Monday meal, snack, or tailgate. Bonus: they are a low-carb, gluten-free food, and can be made with only 5 ingredients!\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Slice a large zucchini 1/4\" thick</li>\r\n	<li>Spray or brush both sides of the zucchini with olive oil</li>\r\n	<li>Broil or grill the zucchini for about 2 minutes each size</li>\r\n	<li>Top with marinara sauce, shredded low-fat mozzarella, salt and pepper</li>\r\n	<li>Broil an additional 2 minutes, being careful not to burn the cheese</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMake these pizzas uniquely yours with shredded peppers, olives, basil, or mini-pepperoni. Let kids decorate pizza bites to their liking. If your zucchini is smaller, cut it in a diagonal direction for a larger surface area.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0011tvD9udTy8I7jbxUV6aMlIvh4_sKeAIGLbkomj7XrM3UiQ4bXrSsP5Bz3nkAcYVgMRQNN70AZMqMbGW6GQzE7lbT8095R84yC_syLPKYRR2aokUKA5h7GTOTdks79TLJQzIKh9u9-3jdv9727Cdkw-p_E6w0RfmHOt1IplSl7cCSvj1ea7QzJIFLvGDEPLN0pqxv8w7I-148rNQiyKKxXPfS57Qrip-t&amp;c=3Neb1x8oCvXYazvdgjkHUftrjbnj96Yq_jxUtKLEbIumwUaXJ5w2iQ==&amp;ch=WXO2tZCDiMqrDGYp-D3oBS5nFNUpNxhxt5DmlMLPRB4DSeoYVR-ITA==\"><em>Click here to get the full recipe from Skinny Taste</em></a>.', 'Zucchini Pizza Bites', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'zucchini-pizza-bites', '', '', '2015-09-21 16:05:17', '2015-09-21 22:05:17', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2372', '0', 'post', '', '0');
