INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2377', '14', '2015-10-06 08:29:54', '2015-10-06 14:29:54', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Road-to-Resiliency.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2382\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Road-to-Resiliency-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Road to Resiliency\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>How do you react to life\'s setbacks? Resiliency is the ability to adapt well over time after potentially stressful or traumatic life-changing events. Bouncing back from a difficult time doesn\'t mean a person hasn\'t walked through emotional pain or distress, but rather they are adapting to the setback and working to overcome adversity. To build resilience:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Reach out to others and accept support from those willing to help.</li>\r\n	<li>Accept what you can\'t change, but change how you react.</li>\r\n	<li>Find meaning in things that give you a sense of accomplishment and purpose.</li>\r\n	<li>Take care of your physical health through exercise and rest.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain a positive outlook of yourself and stay optimistic of the good things that will come in the future.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen self-help and mental toughness aren\'t enough, professional help can keep you functioning through a tough time and help with anxiety, depression, and post-traumatic stress disorder. <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001PboQc0qUVyji43QGlZipBEpBwr1EVVWeHQ44fHxt3DpbN_gRoEx921cAdGyaKwsMGTM4X_tOCLrjMr69N-7CNtN23r3egK13usIufa0pUpIFatM9s8Cvc17tK7f_yOgPSV3sZ_m2_Ery-D8ZwLsdHRzGXvvyQdKD0BT2BPEruS0WaLz_cTf0neaRmOn5_GRJpmfDfyDJUwkMMuBtbn9RStHQIZOa4vcevhBvQefNjFWb0kvHE4WhzmoUNv-rZjvcPT_RG1C8tXQ1RBshqI8wE0ncdYBJK1HG&amp;c=5aH9Yz5McRf1Ar-uaa_atp7q0U5kWxYtWO0XEch4lqI-Ayq0juJtEg==&amp;ch=F6TqsZ750kKJCkNMVKTvqYLQpmI4Xq_cYmD8dEsTBUhA1T_TkO4XmQ==\"><em>More</em></a>', 'The Road to Resiliency', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-road-to-resiliency', '', '', '2015-10-22 08:42:01', '2015-10-22 14:42:01', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2377', '0', 'post', '', '0');
