INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('2389', '14', '2015-10-26 08:44:24', '2015-10-26 14:44:24', '<a href=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/3-2-1-Done.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-2378\" src=\"http://www.sterling-wellness.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/3-2-1-Done-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"3-2-1 Done\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>If you can spare 15 minutes, you can get a total body workout without going to the gym or buying expensive exercise equipment. Customize the workout below to elevate your heart rate and challenge yourself physically:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>5 minutes-</strong> Do any cardiovascular exercise like walking, running in place, or a combination of plyometric exercises like high knees or jumping jacks.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>4 minutes-</strong> Do 1 minute of lunges and 1 minute of mountain climbers. Repeat once.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>3 minutes</strong>- Do 10 push ups and 15 tricep dips. Repeat for a total of 3 minutes.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>2 minutes-</strong> Do 30 seconds of regular squats, then 30 seconds of jump squats. Repeat once.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>1 minute-</strong> Hold a plank position for 60 seconds.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWatching a 30 minute television show? Repeat the workout again to meet the daily activity requirement! <a href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001PboQc0qUVyji43QGlZipBEpBwr1EVVWeHQ44fHxt3DpbN_gRoEx929k-4THcutMX05B6EVz4XKr1Ff4m2zIZSLUyu9EVSs5s7jYQRj8dcPFwtDn1y__KyE3Scw69tyOqV8nqTgD5a6AyhcDx3w0yetDKuiNmApQ4fcKKF9GnexCuuLpCfJnmPGC1SgpxqGYMwj4cVAPvcdUY9Glul1Vr9gnlm84JTbywaJv7gr8d6ee72oAr2D5XXQ==&amp;c=5aH9Yz5McRf1Ar-uaa_atp7q0U5kWxYtWO0XEch4lqI-Ayq0juJtEg==&amp;ch=F6TqsZ750kKJCkNMVKTvqYLQpmI4Xq_cYmD8dEsTBUhA1T_TkO4XmQ==\"><em>More</em></a>', '3-2-1 and Done', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-2-1-and-done', '', '', '2015-10-22 08:45:06', '2015-10-22 14:45:06', '', '0', 'http://www.sterling-wellness.com/?p=2389', '0', 'post', '', '0');
